20housing%20deal%20as%20he%20is%20taking%20out%20bad%20guys.%3Cp%3EInsomniac%20Games%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20Spidey%20Senses%20were%20good.%20He%20got%20a%20great%20deal%2C%26quot%3B%20Rafael%20Reyes%2C%20branch%20manager%20with%20Cross%20Country%20Mortgage%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSecond%20mortgages%20typically%20come%20at%20a%20higher%20rate.%20It%20all%20depends%20on%20what's%20going%20on%20with%20the%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20timing%20wasn't%20the%20best%2C%20he%20probably%20could%20have%20got%20it%20cheaper%20if%20he%20had%20waited%20a%20few%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Reyes%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20he%20did%20really%20well%20for%20where%20the%20market%20was%20at%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAngelo%20Gionis%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20at%20Contour%20Mortgage%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20while%20he%20wouldn't%20say%20it%20was%20a%20super%20deal%2C%20Spider-Man's%20mortgage%20was%20fair%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it%20was%20actually%20a%20second%20mortgage%20Aunt%20May%20took%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%2C%20however%2C%20Aunt%20May%20had%20taken%20out%20a%20home%20equity%20line%20of%20credit%20instead%2C%20Peter%20Parker%20would%20be%20facing%20a%20nightmare%20of%20a%20loan%20with%20a%20rate%20way%20too%20high%20for%20what%20it%20should%20have%20been.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpider-Man%20was%20fortunate.%20Had%20his%20mortgage%20been%20taken%20out%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20later%20in%202020%20or%202021%20with%20that%206.89%25%20interest%20rate%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20a%20terrible%20deal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20those%20years%2C%20the%20rates%20were%20%26quot%3Bartificially%20low%26quot%3B%20thanks%20to%20Federal%20Reserve%20intervention%20to%20stimulate%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20effects%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20Gionis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20thing's%20certain%3A%20If%20Spider-Man's%206.89%25%20mortgage%20was%20taken%20out%20today%2C%20it%20woul