essinsider.com%2Fgeorgia-restaurant-charging-diners-for-misbehaving-kids-slammed-online-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20restaurant%20near%20Blue%20Ridge%2C%20Georgia%20has%20been%20criticized%20on%20Reddit%20for%20adding%20an%20%26quot%3Badult%20surcharge%26quot%3B%20for%20parents%20whose%20kids%20don't%20behave.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeorgia-restaurant-charging-diners-for-misbehaving-kids-slammed-online-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22School%20Textbooks%20To%20Have%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20Instead%20Of%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%3F%20What%20NCERT%20Said%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20replaced%20with%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20school%20textbooks%20for%20all%20classes%2C%20a%20high-level%20committee%20for%20social%20sciences%2C%20constituted%20by%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20(NCERT)%20to%20revise%20the%20school%20curriculum%2C%20has%20recommended.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20committee%20chairperson%20C%20I%20Isaac%2C%20the%20panel%20has%20suggested%20replacing%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BIndia%26quot%3B%20with%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20textbooks%2C%20introducing%20%26quot%3Bclassical%20history%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3Bancient%20history%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20the%20curriculum%20and%20including%20the%20Indian%20Knowledge%20System%20(IKS)%20in%20the%20syllabus%20for%20all%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENCERT%20Chairman%20Dinesh%20Saklani%2C%20however%2C%20said%20no%20decision%20has%20been%20taken%20yet%20on%20the%20panel's%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20committee%20has%20unanimously%20recommended%20that%20the%20name%20'Bharat'%20should%20be%20used%20in%20the%20textbooks%20for%20students%20across%20classes.%20We%20have%20also%20recommended%20introducing%20classical%20history%20instead%20of%20ancient%20history%20in%20the%20textbooks%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaac%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBharat%20is%20an%20age-old%20name.%20The%20name%20Bharat%20has%20been%20used%20in%20ancient%20texts%2C%20such%20as%20Vishnu%20Purana%2C%20which%20is%207%2C000%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaac%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20name%20Bharat%20first%20appeared%20officially%20when%20the%20government%20sent%20out%20G20%20invites%20in%20the%20name%20of%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20Bharat%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20%26quot%3BPresident%20of%20India%26quot%3B.%C2%A0Later%2C%20the%20nameplate%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20during%20the%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20also%20read%20%26quot%3BBharat%26quot%3B%2C%20instead%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsaac%20said%20the%20committee%20has%20also%20recommended%20highlighting%20%26quot%3BHindu%20victories%26quot%3B%20in%20various%20battles%20in%20the%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20failures%20are%20presently%20mentioned%20in%20the%20textbooks.%20But%20our%20victories%20over%20the%20Mughals%20and%20sultans%20are%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Isaac%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Historical%20Research%20(ICHR).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20British%20had%20divided%20Indian%20history%20into%20three%20phases%20--%20ancient%2C%20medieval%20and%20modern%20--%20showing%20India%20in%20darkness%2C%20unaware%20of%20scientific%20knowledge%20and%20progress.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20have%20suggested%20that%20the%20classical%20period%20of%20Indian%20history%20be%20taught%20in%20schools%2C%20along%20with%20medieval%20and%20modern%20periods%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20NCERT%20is%20revising%20the%20curriculum%20of%20the%20school%20textbooks%20in%20line%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%20The%20council%20recently%20constituted%20a%2019-member%20National%20Syllabus%20and%20Teaching%20Learning%20Material%20Committee%20(NSTC)%20to%20finalise%20the%20curriculum%2C%20textbooks%20and%20learning%20material%20for%20these%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20committee%20has%20also%20recommended%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Indian%20Knowledge%20System%20(IKS)%20in%20the%20curriculum%20of%20all%20subjects%2C%26quot%3B%20Isaac%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20members%20of%20the%20committee%20include%20ICHR%20Chairperson%20Raghuvendra%20Tanwar%2C%20Vandana%20Mishra%2C%20Professor%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20(JNU)%2C%20Vasant%20Shinde%2C%20former%20vice-chancellor%20of%20the%20Deccan%20College%20Deemed%20University%2C%20and%20Mamta%20Yadav%2C%20who%20teaches%20sociology%20in%20a%20Haryana%20government%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698231300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2F5jmh35jk_ncert-650_625x300_18_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fschool-textbooks-to-have-bharat-instead-of-india-what-ncert-said-4512288%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20NCERT%20is%20revising%20the%20curriculum%20of%20the%20school%20textbooks%20in%20line%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fschool-textbooks-to-have-bharat-instead-of-india-what-ncert-said-4512288%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fschool-textbooks-to-have-bharat-instead-of-india-what-ncert-said-4512288%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fschool-textbooks-to-have-bharat-instead-of-india-what-ncert-said-4512288%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20Will%20Find%20It%20Hard%20To%20Defend%20L'affaire%20Mahua%20Moitra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOn%20Vijayadashami%20day%2C%20as%20West%20Bengal's%20annual%20religio-cultural%20Durga%20Puja%20festivities%20wound%20down%2C%20Cyclone%20'Hamoon'%20threatened%20the%20coastal%20areas%20of%20the%20state.%20For%20the%20government%20of%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20her%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%2C%20this%20annual%20threat%20of%20nature%20added%20to%20a%20storm%20raging%20for%20the%20past%20fortnight%20over%20l'affaire%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20the%20party's%20MP%20from%20Krishnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrinamool%2C%20which%20is%20quick%20to%20play%20victim%20and%20allege%20the%20misuse%20of%20agencies%20by%20the%20Centre%20when%20scams%20related%20to%20the%20state%20are%20probed%2C%20maintained%20a%20deafening%20silence%20as%20charges%20were%20traded%20on%20what%20has%20come%20to%20be%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bcash-for-query%26quot%3B%20scam.%20(West%20Bengal%20is%20among%20the%20states%20that%20have%20withdrawn%20general%20consent%20to%20the%20CBI%20to%20probe%20cases%20-%20all%20CBI%20probes%20and%20most%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20probes%20in%20the%20state%20are%20being%20conducted%20under%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20is%20using%20these%20agencies%20as%20its%20arm).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20silence%20was%20broken%20four%20days%20back%2C%20not%20voluntarily%20but%20necessitated%20by%20media%20queries.%20Trinamool%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20appeared%20to%20smirk%20as%20he%20told%20television%20cameras%2C%20%26quot%3BTrinamool%20Congress%20has%20nothing%20to%20say%20on%20the%20Mahua%20Moitra%20issue.%20The%20party%20will%20not%20give%20any%20reaction%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGhosh%20hinted%20that%20it%20was%20for%20Mahua%20Moitra%20to%20offer%20clarifications.%20Ghosh%20speaks%20only%20at%20the%20instance%20of%20his%20boss%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20His%20denial%20had%20the%20intrinsic%20hazard%20of%20affirmation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20Ghosh%20chose%20to%20wink%20at%20l'affaire%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20the%20party's%20Rajya%20Sabha%20leader%2C%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20clarified%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20would%20take%20an%20%26quot%3Bappropriate%20decision%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%20took%20up%20BJP%20leader%20Nishikant%20Dubey's%20complaint%20against%20Moitra.%20Calling%20the%20Ethics%20panel%20the%20%26quot%3Bright%20forum%26quot%3B%20for%20investigating%20the%20case%2C%20O'Brien%20said%20Moitra%20had%20been%20counselled%20to%20place%20her%20case%20before%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20not%20the%20last%20from%20the%20Trinamool%20brass.%20A%20day%20after%20O'Brien's%20categorical%20assertion%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Minister%20Firhad%20Hakim%2C%20who%20is%20also%20Mayor%20of%20Kolkata%2C%20seemed%20to%20go%20soft%20on%20Moitra%20and%20endorsed%20her%20stand%20that%20the%20allegations%20were%20aimed%20at%20'silencing'%20her%20in%20parliament.%20Hakim%20was%20quick%20to%20add%20that%20he%20was%20expressing%20his%20%26quot%3Bpersonal%20view%2C%20not%20the%20views%20of%20the%20party%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudip%20Bandyopadhyay%2C%20Trinamool's%20leader%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20preferred%20silence%20on%20the%20MP%20who%20belongs%20to%20this%20House.%20West%20Bengal%20BJP%20leaders%20were%20quick%20to%20seize%20on%20the%20mismatch%20and%20allege%20that%20the%20Trinamool%20is%20divided%20on%20the%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20during%20the%20Durga%20Puja%20festivities%2C%20while%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20and%20her%20party%20were%20silent%20on%20Moitra%2C%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20who%20visited%20Kolkata%20-%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20JP%20Nadda%2C%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%2C%20Tejaswi%20Surya%20-%20too%20avoided%20raising%20the%20topic.%20Their%20focus%20was%20different.%20Durga%20Puja%20pandals%20are%20famed%20for%20their%20unique%20themes.%20The%20Subodh%20Mullick%20Square%20Puja%20pandal%2C%20organised%20by%20a%20BJP%20councillor%2C%20was%20built%20like%20a%20replica%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20coming%20up%20in%20Ayodhya.%20It%20drew%20the%20maximum%20crowds%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20stoic%20silence%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20perhaps%20fancies%20holding%20the%20copyright%20on%20%26quot%3Bexposing%20the%20Modi-Adani%20nexus%26quot%3B%2C%20is%20also%20worth%20noting.%20Sanjay%20Raut%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20Tejaswi%20Yadav%20of%20(RJD)%20apart%2C%20no%20member%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20come%20to%20Mahua%20Moitra's%20defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20expos%C3%A9%20by%20lawyer%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai%20(referred%20to%20as%20jilted%20ex%20by%20Moitra)%2C%20its%20escalation%20by%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20and%20the%20affirmation%20of%20their%20charges%20by%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20in%20an%20affidavit%20to%20the%20Consul%20General%20of%20India%20in%20Dubai%20(where%20he%20is%20resident)%20seem%20to%20have%20stunned%20the%20political%20class%20into%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20is%20battling%20a%20number%20of%20scams.%20Alleged%20corruption%20in%20the%20recruitment%20of%20teachers%3B%20selections%20in%20municipal%20jobs%3B%20coal%20and%20cattle%20smuggling%20(to%20Bangladesh)%20are%20weighing%20heavily%20on%20the%20party.%20Apparently%2C%20it%20does%20not%20want%20to%20add%20to%20the%20list%20l'affaire%20Mahua%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20a%2015-member%20body%20with%20seven%20BJP%20and%20eight%20opposition%20members%2C%20will%20now%20take%20up%20Nishikant%20Dubey's%20complaint.%20By%20month-end%2C%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20will%20resume%20hearing%20the%20defamation%20suit%20filed%20by%20Moitra%20against%20Dubey%2C%20the%20whistleblower-lawyer%20Dehadrai%2C%20and%20against%20media%20entities%20that%20have%20reported%20the%20story.%20The%20initial%20hearing%20had%20to%20be%20aborted%20as%20Moitra's%20lawyer%20had%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20case%20over%20issues%20related%20to%20ethics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EL'affaire%20Moitra%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20India's%20parliamentary%20history.%20The%20cash-for-query%20scam%20of%202005%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20expulsion%20of%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20and%20the%20resignation%20of%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%2C%20was%20exposed%20through%20a%20sting%20operation%20by%20the%20media.%20The%20Dehadrai%20allegations%2C%20which%20suggest%20that%20an%20MP's%20parliamentary%20password%20was%20compromised%2C%20enabling%20a%20businessman%20to%20directly%20frame%20and%20submit%20questions%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20portal%2C%20merit%20a%20thorough%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20has%20countered%20that%20many%20more%20MPs%20share%20their%20passwords%20with%20unauthorised%20persons.%20Dehadrai's%20sworn%20affidavit%20clearly%20pinpoints%20the%20arrow%20of%20suspicion.%20If%20more%20such%20examples%20are%20identified%2C%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20and%20appropriate%20probe%20bodies%20could%20unearth%20more%20worms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%2C%20the%20state%20Mahua%20Moitra%20represents%2C%20has%20sent%20legendary%20women%20parliamentarians%20in%20the%20past-Renu%20Chakraborty%20and%20Geeta%20Mukherjee%2C%20both%20belonging%20to%20the%20now-defunct%20CPI%2C%20were%20among%20them.%20As%20the%20new%20Parliament%20House%20began%20its%20journey%20with%20legislation%20enabling%20reservation%20for%20women%2C%20MPs%20across%20the%20political%20divide%20recalled%20the%20pioneering%20role%20of%20Geeta%20Mukherjee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20dominance%20of%20Bengal%20politics%2C%20the%20state%20sent%2014%20women%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%202014%20out%20of%20its%2042%20seats%20-%20that%20came%20to%2033%20per%20cent%2C%20even%20without%20reservation.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20number%20dropped%20to%2011%2C%20but%20was%20still%20above%20the%20average%20representation%20for%20women%20from%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20of%20martyrs%20Pritilata%20Waddedar%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20Surya%20Sen%20of%20the%20Chittagong%20armoury%20raid%20fame%2C%20and%20her%20comrade%20Kalpana%20Dutt%2C%20along%20with%20Matangini%20Hazra%20-%20who%20did%20not%20let%20the%20tricolour%20fall%20to%20the%20ground%20even%20as%20she%20was%20shot%20dead%20-%20are%20the%20ideals%20for%20women%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20So%20are%20Sarojini%20Naidu%20(n%C3%A9e%20Chattopadhyaya)%20and%20Aruna%20Asaf%20Ali%20(n%C3%A9e%20Ganguly)%2C%20whose%20roles%20in%20the%20freedom%20movement%20are%20remembered.%20Against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20Moitra's%20Louis%20Vuitton%20persona%20will%20perhaps%20be%20a%20tad%20difficult%20for%20the%20Trinamool%20to%20explain%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20Editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698230940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fepj642fk_mahua-moitra-getty_625x300_20_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmamata-banerjee-will-find-it-hard-to-defend-laffair-mahua-moitra-4511371%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trinamool%2C%20which%20is%20quick%20to%20play%20victim%20and%20allege%20the%20misuse%20of%20agencies%20by%20the%20Centre%20when%20scams%20related%20to%20the%20state%20are%20probed%2C%20maintained%20a%20deafening%20silence%20as%20charges%20were%20traded%20on%20what%20has%20come%20to%20be%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bcash-for-query%26quot%3B%20scam.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmamata-banerjee-will-find-it-hard-to-defend-laffair-mahua-moitra-4511371%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20Xi%20hails