%5C%22%3Enot%20guaranteed%20a%20living%20wage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20think%20the%20ethical%20thing%20is%20to%20tip%20drivers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20should%20generally%20tip%20your%20driver%20at%20least%2015%25%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeff%20Hoenig%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65381f3496f7540cd0646967%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeff%20Hoenig%3Cp%3EJeff%20Hoenig%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20Leighton%2C%20an%20etiquette%20expert%20and%20co-host%20of%20the%20podcast%20%26quot%3BWere%20You%20Raised%20By%20Wolves%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20Insider%20that%20tipping%20between%2015%25%20and%2020%25%20is%20the%20general%20recommendation%20for%20Uber%20and%20Lyft%20drivers%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you've%20done%20something%20that%20has%20made%20the%20ride%20less%20pleasant%20for%20the%20driver%2C%20such%20as%20watching%20YouTube%20videos%20without%20headphones%20at%20full%20blast%20or%20spilling%20food%20on%20the%20seats%2C%20then%20a%20larger%20tip%20is%20also%20a%20good%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarley%20said%2020%25%20should%20be%20the%20standard%20tip%2C%20but%20that%20customers%20who%20feel%20the%20driver%20went%20above%20and%20beyond%20should%20consider%20tipping%2025%25%20or%20more.%20For%20short%20rides%20that%20cost%20under%20%2410%2C%20he%20said%20Americans%20should%20tip%20at%20least%20%242%20as%20a%20baseline%20and%20no%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Hoenig%2C%20a%2063-year-old%20part-time%20Uber%20driver%20in%20South%20Carolina%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20roughly%20half%20of%20his%20customers%20left%20a%20tip%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20said%20a%20%243%20tip%20is%20reasonable%20for%20most%20rides%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20types%20of%20trips%20where%20he%20thinks%20a%20bigger%20tip%20%E2%80%94%20of%20at%20least%20%245%20%E2%80%94%20is%20particularly%20warranted.%20These%20include%20rides%20that%20are%20to-and-from%20the%20airport%2C%20late%20at%20night%20or%20early%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20over%20an%20hour%20long%2C%20or%20involve%20the%20driver%20loading%20or%20unloading%20something%20from%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hoenig%20said%20even%20a%20%241%20tip%20would%20be%20appreciated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20all%20the%20riders%20who%20don't%20tip%2C%20started%20tipping%20%241%2C%20drivers%20would%20be%20happy%20with%20the%20extra%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ets-Hokin%20gets%20tipped%2C%20he%20said%20it%20typically%20averages%20between%2085%20and%2015%25.%20He%20said%20he%20thinks%20it%20should%20be%20at%20least%2010%25%20to%2020%25%20as%20long%20as%20the%20ride%20has%20met%20the%20customer's%20basic%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInflation%20shouldn't%20stop%20you%20from%20tipping%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gabe%20Ets-Hokin%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65381f510487ff031cad26b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGabe%20Ets-Hokin%3Cp%3EGabe%20Ets-Hokin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20Americans'%20wallets%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-recession-us-economy-outlook-employment-fed-interest-rates-blackrock-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eimpacted%20by%20inflation%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Farley%20said%20this%20shouldn't%20prevent%20them%20from%20tipping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne's%20personal%20finances%20should%20not%20prevent%20a%20passenger%20from%20tipping%20at%20least%20the%20minimum%20acceptable%20percentage%2C%20though%20they%20may%20influence%20the%20frequency%20with%20which%20one%20uses%20a%20ride-share%20app%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20aff