nies%20like%20Zillow%20and%20Trulia%20revolutionized%20home%20search%2C%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20process%20remains%20pretty%20much%20the%20same.%20The%20next%20big%20change%3A%20a%20race%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Amazon%20of%20real%20estate.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMyriam%20Wares%20for%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20a%20home%20has%20never%20been%20simple.%20Sites%20like%20Zillow%20and%20Trulia%20can%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20search%20for%20houses%20online%2C%20but%20even%20if%20you%20find%20the%20right%20home%2C%20that's%20just%20the%20start.%20To%20get%20an%20offer%20together%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20consult%20an%20agent%2C%20apply%20for%20a%20mortgage%2C%20and%20try%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20much%20you%20can%20reasonably%20stretch%20your%20budget.%20Even%20after%20making%20the%20financial%20pitch%2C%20you'll%20find%20a%20crowd%20of%20middlemen%20waiting%20with%20outstretched%20hands%3A%20brokers%2C%20inspectors%2C%20appraisers%2C%20loan%20processors%2C%20credit%20companies%2C%20and%20surveyors.%20That%20all%20sound%20overwhelming%3F%20Well%2C%20you're%20not%20done%20yet.%20Depending%20on%20where%20you%20live%20and%20who%20you%20work%20with%2C%20you%20may%20need%20a%20real-estate%20attorney%2C%20a%20title%20agent%2C%20an%20escrow%20agent%2C%20or%20some%20combination%20of%20the%20three.%20As%20one%20consumer%20advocate%20told%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20almost%20have%20to%20get%20a%20license%20to%20understand%20the%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDecades%20of%20mounting%20regulations%2C%20an%20influx%20of%20new%20players%20in%20the%20industry%2C%20and%20the%20fallout%20from%20the%20housing%20market's%20collapse%20in%202008%20have%20made%20real-estate%20transactions%20increasingly%20bloated%20with%20paperwork%20and%20intermediaries.%20Companies%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fproptech-real-estate-startups-let-down-investors-customers-employees-2023-1%5C%22%3Eraised%20billions%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20promising%20to%20make%20the%20thornier%20parts%20of%20the%20homebuying%20process%20smoother.%20But%20after%20years%20of%20trying%2C%20the%20basic%20structure%20of%20buying%20and%20selling%20a%20home%20remains%20pretty%20much%20the%20same.%20In%20fact%2C%20with%20so%20many%20startups%20trying%20to%20update%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20transaction%20for%20the%20digital%20age%2C%20buying%20a%20home%20has%20actually%20gotten%20more%20complicated.%20Today's%20house%20hunters%20don't%20just%20face%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fus-housing-market-inventory-shortage-high-mortgage-rates-slowdown-prices-2023-6%5C%22%3Einventory%20shortage%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomers-are-happy-interest-rates-home-prices-2023-9%5C%22%3Erising%20mortgage%20rates%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20also%20up%20against%20information%20overload.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20you%2C%20'Yes%2C%20technology%20is%20really%20changing%20it%2C%20and%20it's%20helped%20here%2C%20and%20it's%20improved%20that%2C'%26quot%3B%20Mike%20DelPrete%2C%20a%20scholar-in-residence%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Colorado%20Boulder%20who%20studies%20the%20intersection%20of%20tech%20and%20real%20estate%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%20has%20not%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20better%20way%20is%20possible.%20Companies%20are%20racing%20to%20develop%20platforms%20that%20guide%20users%20seamlessly%20from%20beginning%20to%20end%20of%20a%20home%20purchase.%20Other%20changes%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbad-real-estate-agents-realtors-homebuyers-sellers-housing-market-2023-7%5C%22%3Ehigher%20standards%20for%20real-estate%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20more%20transparent%20agent%20commissions%2C%20could%20make%20things%20simpler%20for%20homebuyers%20who%20are%20currently%20faced%20with%20a%20complex%2C%20overwhelming%2C%20and%20oftentimes%20frustrating%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20general%20rule%2C%20the%20idea%20is%2C%20'If%20it%20ain't%20broke%2C%20don't%20fix%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20Rob%20Hahn%2C%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20longtime%20consultant%20to%20local%20Realtor%20associations%2C%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20I%20think%20it%20is%20kind%20of%20broken.'%20And%20I%20think%20the%20pandemic%20really%20showed%20us%20how%20broken%20it%20is.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20buying%20a%20house%20is%20so%20complicated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20most%20basic%20level%2C%20home%20sales%20are%20complicated%20because%20%3Cem%3Epeople%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20complicated.%20Buying%20a%20house%20is%20often%20the%20largest%20purchase%20someone%20will%20make%20in%20their%20lifetime.%20Each%20buyer%20comes%20to%20this%20monumental%20transaction%20with%20their%20own%20search%20criteria%20and%20financial%20history%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20to%20take%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20approach.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBuying%20and%20selling%20a%20home%20is%20fundamentally%20different%20than%20every%20other%20transaction%2C%26quot%3B%20DelPrete%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BFull%20stop.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheer%20financial%20scale%20of%20homebuying%20is%20a%20good%20reason%20to%20make%20it%20more%20complex%20than%2C%20say%2C%20buying%20a%20gallon%20of%20milk%20or%20a%20car.%20Even%20if%20you%20accept%20a%20bit%20of%20intricacy%2C%20real%20estate%20remains%20a%20stodgy%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20and%20regulation%20is%20at%20the%20core%20of%20that%20resistance%20to%20change.%20Property%20sales%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis%2C%20are%20enmeshed%20in%20a%20dense%20web%20of%20national%20and%20state%20laws.%20Many%20of%20these%20rules%20are%20necessary%20to%20protect%20consumers%20from%20getting%20ripped%20off%2C%20but%20in%20some%20cases%20they%20can%20also%20overcomplicate%20the%20process.%20It%20might%20seem%20more%20efficient%20if%20the%20company%20helping%20you%20find%20a%20home%20could%20also%20hook%20you%20up%20with%20a%20mortgage%20and%20home%20insurance%20and%20handle%20your%20appraisal%20and%20inspection.%20But%20that%20kind%20of%20setup%20could%20leave%20consumers%20vulnerable%20to%20being%20overcharged%20and%20underserved.%20There%20are%20strict%20rules%20to%20limit%20kickbacks%20between%20agents%2C%20mortgage%20lenders%2C%20and%20title%20companies%2C%20for%20example%2C%20so%20that%20buyers%20aren't%20aggressively%20steered%20toward%20certain%20firms%20just%20because%20money%20is%20being%20exchanged%20behind%20their%20backs.%20But%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20it%20doesn't%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20take%20the%20home-appraisal%20process.%20Mortgage%20lenders%20used%20to%20hire%20an%20appraiser%20directly%20to%20value%20the%20house%20and%20help%20determine%20how%20much%20money%20they'd%20be%20willing%20to%20loan%20for%20it.%20But%20lenders%20ended%20up%20abusing%20this%20power%2C%20putting%20pressure%20on%20appraisers%20to%20value%20properties%20higher%20to%20drive%20up%20prices.%20Regulations%20required%20a%20separation%20between%20the%20lenders%20and%20appraisers%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20a%20new%20class%20of%20independent%20middlemen%3A%20appraisal-management%20companies.%20These%20firms%20are%20hired%20by%20a%20lender%20to%20find%20an%20appraiser%20to%20do%20the%20job%2C%20pocketing%20a%20cut%20of%20the%20money%20for%20their%20services.%20Does%20this%20ward%20off%20bad%20behavior%3F%20In%20some%20cases.%20But%20it%20also%20adds%20time%20and%20costs%20to%20the%20process%2C%20an%20extra%20step%20that%20most%20buyers%20probably%20don't%20even%20know%20about.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20clear%20that%20these%20rules%20are%20weighing%20on%20potential%20buyers.%20A%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nar.realtor%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fdocuments%2F2023-home-buyers-and-sellers-generational-trends-report-03-28-2023.pdf%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20homebuyers%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Realtors%20found%20that%2030%25%20of%20respondents%20between%20the%20ages%2024%20and%2032%20%E2%80%94%20the%20cohort%20most%20likely%20to%20include%20first-time%20buyers%20%E2%80%94%20said%20understanding%20the%20process%20was%20the%20most%20difficult%20part%20of%20the%20purchase.%20In%20another%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zillow.com%2Fagent-resources%2Fagent-toolkit%2Ffirst-time-home-buyers-checklist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Zillow%2C%2024%25%20of%20buyers%20said%20they%20didn't%20completely%20understand%20everything%20they%20signed%20when%20buying%20a%20home.%20The%20various%20hoops%20buyers%20have%20to%20jump%20through%20also%20add%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20a%20purchase%3A%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20typical%20homebuyer%20with%20a%20mortgage%20spent%20a%20little%20over%20%244%2C000%2C%20or%201%25%20of%20the%20average%20sale%20price%2C%20on%20closing%20costs%20like%20the%20appraisal%2C%20title%20insurance%2C%20and%20recording%20fees%2C%20said%20ClosingCorp%2C%20a%20provider%20of%20real-estate%20closing-cost%20data.%20Taxes%2C%20which%20are%20usually%20paid%20by%20the%20seller%2C%20added%20another%20%243%2C200.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20challenge%20of%20digitizing%20an%20old-school%20process.%20People%20may%20like%20to%20rent%20a%20movie%20or%20buy%20a%20pizza%20with%20the%20click%20of%20a%20button%2C%20but%20that%20doesn't%20mean%20they%20want%20the%20same%20experience%20for%20a%20home%20purchase%2C%20DelPrete%20told%20me.%20Sure%2C%20people%20can%20tour%20homes%20with%20a%20virtual-reality%20headset%2C%20but%20buyers%20still%20want%20to%20walk%20around%20in%20a%20house%20before%20they%20make%20an%20offer.%20And%20once%20they%20start%20to%20envision%20themselves%20welcoming%20guests%20into%20the%20living%20room%20or%20watching%20their%20kids%20play%20in%20the%20backyard%2C%20they're%20practically%20guaranteed%20to%20act%20irrationally.%20That's%20when%20it's%20helpful%20to%20have%20a%20living%2C%20breathing%20person%20there%20to%20offer%20a%20levelheaded%20perspective.%20Despite%20the%20best%20efforts%20of%20would-be%20disruptors%20to%20cut%20out%20this%20middleman%2C%2088%25%20of%20buyers%20this%20year%20enlisted%20a%20real-estate%20agent%2C%20a%20Zillow%20survey%20found.%20That%20figure%20is%20even%20higher%20than%20it%20was%20prior%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%20in%202019%2C%20when%2082%25%20of%20buyers%20used%20an%20agent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cq%3EPeople%20are%20talking%20about%20launching%20manned%20missions%20to%20Mars%2C%20but%20we're%20actually%20still%20in%20the%20Stone%20Ages%20here%3C%2Fq%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20some%20of%20the%20more%20minor%20attempts%20to%20update%20the%20process%20have%20been%20met%20with%20much%20hand-wringing.%20Take%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20various%20laws%20around%20electronic%20signatures.%20The%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hastened%20the%20adoption%20of%20remote%20online%20notarization%2C%20which%20allows%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20to%20close%20a%20deal%20without%20having%20to%20go%20to%20an%20office%20and%20sign%20paperwork.%20But%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20and%20seven%20states%2C%20including%20California%20and%20Georgia%2C%20still%20don't%20allow%20fully%20remote%20closings%20because%20of%20legal%20hiccups%20or%20fraud%20concerns%20%E2%80%94%20an%20indication%20of%20just%20how%20fragmented%20the%20industry%20is%20and%20how%20slowly%20it%20can%20move%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20adopting%20new%20technology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20talking%20about%20launching%20manned%20missions%20to%20Mars%2C%20but%20we're%20actually%20still%20in%20the%20Stone%20Ages%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20DelPrete%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20the%20caves%2C%20trying%20to%20create%20fire%20and%20get%20everybody%20to%20do%20electronic%20signatures.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20ways%2C%20tech%20has%20made%20the%20process%20of%20buying%20a%20home%20in%202023%20harder%20than%20it%20was%20in%202003%2C%20%26quot%3Bdespite%20a%20lot%20of%20smart%20people%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20spending%20two%20decades%20trying%20to%20make%20it%20easier%2C%26quot%3B%20John%20Berkowitz%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Ojo%2C%20which%20owns%20the%20home-search%20and%20guidance%20site%20Movoto%2C%20told%20me.%20Consumers%20today%20are%20flooded%20with%20options%20thanks%20to%20the%20many%20startups%20that%20have%20jumped%20in%20to%20help%20buyers%20do%20things%20like%20get%20a%20mortgage%20online%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-cash-offer-win-home-bidding-war-startups-mortgage-2022-3%5C%22%3Ebuy%20a%20home%20with%20a%20cash-backed%20offer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20theory%2C%20more%20options%20should%20be%20a%20good%20thing%2C%20but%20that%20hasn't%20been%20the%20case%20in%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20have%20no%20idea%20what%20you're%20doing%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20know%20who%20to%20trust%2C%20more%20choice%20is%20just%20overwhelming%2C%26quot%3B%20Berkowitz%20said.%20And%20because%20all%20these%20companies%20are%20spending%20on%20marketing%20and%20referral%20fees%20to%20acquire%20customers%2C%20those%20costs%20end%20up%20being%20funneled%20down%20to%20buyers%20and%20sellers.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20actually%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20of%20bad%20intentions%20%E2%80%94%20making%20it%20harder%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20things%20change%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20players%20have%20tried%20plenty%20of%20strategies%20to%20bring%20homebuying%20out%20of%20the%20dark%20ages%2C%20but%20any%20changes%20that%20occur%20won't%20involve%20cutting%20corners.%20All%20the%20paperwork%2C%20while%20a%20headache%2C%20is%20designed%20to%20make%20sure%20inexperienced%20buyers%20and%20sellers%20are%20aware%20of%20the%20costs%20involved%20and%20aren't%20being%20screwed%20over%20by%20much%20more%20sophisticated%2C%20nefarious%20players.%20Twenty%20years%20after%20the%20advent%20of%20online%20home%20searches%2C%20the%20next%20step%20in%20innovation%2C%20Berkowitz%20told%20me%2C%20will%20be%20focused%20on%20assembling%20all%20the%20pieces%20of%20the%20real-estate%20transaction%20in%20one%20place%20%E2%80%94%20a%20one-stop%20shop%20where%20customers%20can%20enter%20their%20information%20and%20then%20find%20the%20best%20providers%20to%20work%20with%20at%20each%20step%20in%20the%20journey.%20The%20secret%20sauce%20that%20companies%20are%20chasing%20would%20involve%20matching%20someone%20with%20the%20right%20agent%2C%20the%20right%20lender%2C%20and%20then%20all%20the%20other%20parties%20along%20the%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBobby%20Bryant%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20the%20real-estate%20tech%20firm%20Doss%20Group%20Inc.%2C%20envisions%20an%20app%20in%20which%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20search%2C%20mortgage%2C%20insurance%20%E2%80%94%20is%20available%20as%20a%20seamless%20experience%20for%20consumers.%20He%20compared%20it%20to%20calling%20an%20Uber%3A%20It%20may%20feel%20quick%20and%20easy%20for%20a%20consumer%2C%20but%20the%20company%20controlling%20the%20app%20still%20has%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20old-school%20components%20of%20a%20physical%20driver%20getting%20from%20point%20A%20to%20point%20B%20while%20obeying%20traffic%20rules%20along%20the%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20does%20one%20create%20the%20Amazon%20of%20real%20estate%3F%26quot%3B%20Bryant%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20almost%20do%20it%20by%20way%20of%20creating%20a%20super%20app%20that%20brings%20it%20together%2C%20streamline%20the%20process%2C%20and%20make%20it%20more%20economical%2C%20easier%20for%20everybody%20involved.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZillow%2C%20which%20has%20already%20helped%20make%20the%20initial%20search%20for%20a%20home%20easier%2C%20is%20trying%20to%20make%20this%20dream%20a%20reality.%20The%20company%20has%20spent%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20year