s%20against%20asking%20for%20a%20raise%2C%20staying%20after%20a%20PIP%2C%20and%20other%20career-jeopardizing%20mistakes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Williams%20is%20the%20former%20VP%20of%20HR%20at%20Microsoft.%20In%20his%20more%20than%2040%20years%20in%20business%20and%20leadership%2C%20he's%20seen%20employees%20and%20leaders%20make%20the%20same%20ill-advised%20decisions%2C%20regardless%20of%20seniority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20four%20career%20mistakes%20he%20says%20to%20avoid%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMistake%201%3A%20Threatening%20to%20quit%20the%20company%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20frustration%2C%20many%20employees%20issue%20an%20ultimatum%20and%20threaten%20to%20leave%20the%20company%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20get%20a%20higher%20salary%20or%20a%20better%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20explains%20that%20this%20rarely%20goes%20how%20the%20employee%20hopes.%20Surprising%20your%20manager%20with%20the%20threat%20may%20make%20you%20seem%20rash%20and%20irrational.%20If%20you've%20complained%20before%2C%20you%20seem%20to%20be%20throwing%20a%20long%2C%20extended%20tantrum.%20A%20manager%20may%20also%20see%20it%20as%20a%20resignation%20in%20disguise%20and%20assume%20you're%20on%20the%20way%20out%20anyway%20%E2%80%94%20no%20matter%20what%20they%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20concludes%20that%20once%20you%20make%20the%20threat%2C%20you've%20already%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20more%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-really-happens-when-you-threaten-to-leave-your-job-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EWhat%20actually%20happens%20when%20you%20threaten%20to%20quit%20over%20another%20job%20offer%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMistake%202%3A%20Asking%20for%20a%20raise%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20asking%20for%20a%20raise%2C%20you're%20already%20starting%20from%20a%20position%20of%20weakness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20raise%20shouldn't%20be%20a%20favor.%20Don't%20bring%20up%20market%20value%2C%20what%20other%20people%20are%20paid%2C%20or%20that%20you%20have%20a%20family%20to%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Williams%20recommends%20treating%20the%20conversation%20like%20a%20value%20exchange.%20Figure%20out%20the%20value%20you%20generate%20for%20the%20company%2C%20such%20as%20the%20revenue%20you%20produce%20or%20the%20savings%20you%20create.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20More%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-employee-things-i-would-never-do-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHere%20are%204%20things%20I%20would%20never%20do%20as%20an%20employee%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMistake%203%3A%20Not%20making%20your%20boss%20your%20ally%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20says%20that%20your%20boss%20is%20your%20best%20ally%20at%20work.%20You%20want%20someone%20on%20your%20side%20who%20will%20be%20in%20the%20room%20when%20decisions%20are%20made%20about%20layoffs%2C%20promotions%2C%20and%20raises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20your%20bosses%20best%20friend%20to%20gain%20their%20favor.%20But%20there%20are%20several%20keys%20to%20winning%20them%20over.%20Williams%20advises%20employees%20to%20speak%20up%20about%20their%20accomplishments%20in%20one-on-one%20meetings%2C%20look%20for%20tasks%20to%20knock%20off%20their%20boss'%20plate%2C%20and%20be%20supportive%20of%20their%20boss%20and%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20more%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvp-at-microsoft-how-to-make-boss-your-ally-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EYour%20boss%20is%20your%20most%20important%20ally%20at%20work.%20Here's%20how%20to%20win%20them%20over.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMistake%204%3A%20Staying%20at%20a%20company%20once%20you've%20been%20placed%20on%20a%20PIP%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20get%20put%20on%20a%20PIP%2C%20you%20should%20immediately%20consider%20leaving%20your%20company.%20The%20shadow%20of%20a%20PIP%20will%20be%20a%20weight%20on%20your%20success%20if%20you%20stay%20at%20the%20same%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERarely%20is%20a%20PIP%20actually%20a%20plan%20to%20help%20you%20recover%20and%20improve%20your%20job%20performance%2C%20Williams%20writes.%20It's%20best%20to%20leave%20and%20start%20with%20a%20clean%20slate%20somewhere%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20more%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-do-if-placed-on-pip-microsoft-vp-leave-asap-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EYou%20should%20leave%20a%20company%20right%20away%20if%20you%20get%20put%20on%20a%20PIP%3A%20'Surviving%20it%20is%20like%20a%20sign%20on%20your%20back'%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-mistakes-to-avoid-from-former-microsoft-vp-of-hr-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698225781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653825be356802a56be2b60f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-mistakes-to-avoid-from-former-microsoft-vp-of-hr-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20make%20career%20mistakes%20without%20realizing%20it.%20Chris%20Williams%2C%20former%20VP%20of%20HR%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20explains%20what%20to%20avoid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jgyimesi%40insider.com%20(Jenna%20Gyimesi%20)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-mistakes-to-avoid-from-former-microsoft-vp-of-hr-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Alia%20wishes%20mom%20Soni%20on%20her%20birthday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698225763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104695096%2Cimgsize-110930.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com