ff031cac1af7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Enull%3Cp%3EArantza%20Pena%20Popo%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20Planet%20Fitness%20CEO%20Chris%20Rondeau%20was%20fired%2C%20it%20was%20a%20surprise%20to%20nearly%20everyone.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20former%20employees%20tell%20Insider%20Rondeau's%20behavior%20raised%20eyebrows%20among%20some%20at%20headquarters.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFormer%20staff%20say%20he%20kept%20a%20keg%20in%20his%20office%20and%20had%20assistants%20withdraw%20thousands%20in%20cash%20from%20his%20personal%20account%20for%20travel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplanet-fitness-ceo-chris-rondeau-fired-gym-plnt-stock-price-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%3Cspan%3EChris%20Rondeau%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20ten-year%20CEO%20of%20Planet%20Fitness%2C%20was%20fired%20by%20the%20company's%20board%20of%20directors%2C%20he%20told%20Insider%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bseriously%20blindsided.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20finished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider%20in%20a%20text%20message%20last%20month.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20the%20best%20team%20best%20franchisees%20and%20an%20amazing%20business.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConfusion%20over%20Rondeau's%20abrupt%20departure%20sent%20shares%20for%20the%20largest%20gym%20network%20in%20the%20US%20plummeting%20by%2020%25%2C%20slicing%20off%20more%20than%20%241%20billion%20in%20market%20cap.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20exact%20reasons%20behind%20the%20board's%20decision%20are%20still%20unclear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20questions%20about%20Rondeau's%20departure%20continue%20to%20go%20unanswered%2C%20Insider%20has%20learned%20that%20his%20hard-partying%20ways%20raised%20eyebrows%20among%20some%20staff.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInsider%20spoke%20with%20six%20former%20Planet%20Fitness%20employees.%20Some%20former%20staffers%20pointed%20to%20drinking%20in%20the%20office%20and%20Rondeau%20asking%20company%20staff%20to%20withdraw%20thousands%20from%20Rondeau's%20personal%20accounts%20to%20pay%20for%20cash-fueled%20weekend%20getaways%20%E2%80%94%20even%20after%20a%20lawsuit%20claimed%20Planet%20Fitness%20suffered%20from%20a%20%26quot%3Bdebaucherous%26quot%3B%20alcohol-fueled%20environment%20%E2%80%94%20as%20red%20flags.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPlanet%20Fitness%20and%20Rondeau%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Former%20Planet%20Fitness%20CEO%20Chris%20Rondeau%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20in%202015%20after%20the%20company's%20IPO.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6537f53e356802a56be25d2d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20Planet%20Fitness%20CEO%20Chris%20Rondeau%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20in%202015%2C%20after%20the%20company's%20IPO.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Drew%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cspan%3EKegs%20and%20cash%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20former%20employees%20confirmed%20Rondeau%20kept%20a%20keg%20in%20his%20office%20at%20Planet%20Fitness%20headquarters%20in%20Hampton%2C%20New%20Hampshire.%20A%20former%20employee%20told%20Insider%20she%20felt%20the%20keg%20was%20unprofessional%2C%20while%20a%20former%20executive%20assistant%20defended%20it%2C%20saying%20the%20keg%20was%20%26quot%3Blocked%20and%20frequently%20untouched.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%202018%20workplace%20lawsuit%20against%20Rondeau%20and%20other%20executives%2C%20former%20employee%20Casey%20Willard%20said%20drinking%20on%20the%20job%20was%20encouraged%2C%20describing%20events%20like%20%26quot%3BFireball%20Fridays%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBeers%20with%20Peers%26quot%3B%20that%20sometimes%20started%20before%208%3A30%20AM.%20In%20court%2C%20lawyers%20for%20Rondeau%20denied%20claims%20about%20debauchery%20but%20said%20%26quot%3Bsome%20employees%20periodically%20consumed%20alcohol%20during%20work%20hours%20at%20certain%20times.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20drank%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20third%20former%20employee%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20most%20toxic%2C%20high-school%20environment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20two%20former%20employees%20who%20recalled%20a%20keg%20being%20in%20Rondeau's%20office%20said%20drinking%20that%20took%20place%20at%20work%20wasn't%20compulsory%20or%20disruptive.%20Willard's%20lawsuit%20didn't%20prompt%20the%20keg's%20removal%2C%20either%3B%20it%20remained%20there%20even%20after%20the%20lawsuit%20was%20filed%2C%20one%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20employees%20also%20told%20Insider%20Rondeau%20would%20ask%20assistants%2C%20who%20were%20company%20employees%2C%20to%20obtain%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20cash%20ahead%20of%20leisure%20trips%20he%20asked%20them%20to%20coordinate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20executive%20assistant%20for%20Rondeau%20said%20he%20used%20the%20cash%2C%20taken%20from%20his%20personal%20bank%20accounts%2C%20to%20tip%20when%20he%20went%20to%20dinner%20or%20to%20buy%20coffee%20from%20Dunkin%20Donuts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20a%20generous%20tipper%2C%20there's%20no%20denying%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20executive%20assistant%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20didn't%20think%20the%20amount%20of%20cash%20Rondeau%20traveled%20with%20was%20excessive%20for%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20publicly%20traded%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERondeau%20would%20travel%20with%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20in%20cash%20on%20trips%20spanning%20a%20single%20weekend%2C%20another%20former%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20former%20employee%20said%20these%20trips%20often%20blurred%20the%20line%20between%20leisure%20and%20business.%20Rondeau%20would%20often%20meet%20with%20franchise%20owners%20on%20the%20trips%2C%20people%20with%20whom%20he%20had%20both%20professional%20and%20personal%20relationships%2C%20the%20former%20employee%20recalled.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERondeau's%20separation%20agreement%20bars%20him%20from%20contacting%20any%20Planet%20Fitness%20employees%20about%20his%20employment%2C%20except%20those%20in%20the%20legal%20or%20human-resources%20divisions%20per%20his%20separation%20agreement%2C%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20Planet%20Fitness%20previously%20told%20Insider%20Rondeau's%20departure%20was%20not%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bany%20material%20or%20unexpected%20financial%20events.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20September%20earnings%20call%20made%20shortly%20before%20Rondeau's%20ouster%20painted%20an%20upbeat%20picture%20of%20the%20company's%20business%20prospects%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20company's%20same-store%20sales%20rose%20nearly%209%25%20last%20quarter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20gym's%20dirt-cheap%20pricing%20scheme%20%E2%80%94%20just%20%2410%20a%20month%20to%20join%20%E2%80%94%20had%20increasingly%20come%20under%20scrutiny%20as%20inflation%20drove%20up%20prices.%20In%20what%20would%20be%20his%20final%20earnings%20call%20as%20CEO%2C%20Rondeau%20said%20he%20wouldn't%20budge%20on%20the%20%2410-a-month%20pricing%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20%26quot%3Bcheapen%20the%20brand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERondeau%20was%20a%20fixture%20at%20Planet%20Fitness%2C%20starting%20front%20desk%20associate%20at%20the%20company's%20first%20gym%20in%201993%20and%20ascending%20to%20CEO%20in%202013%20%E2%80%94%20but%20his%20tenure%20had%20roug