0armed%20forces%2C%20the%20former%20Northern%20and%20Central%20Army%20Commander%20goes%20on%20to%20state%2C%20were%20a%20constitutional%20instrument%20controlled%20by%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20and%20any%20mandated%20social%20work%20initiative%20that%20smacked%20of%20political%20intent%20was%20an%20%E2%80%98encroachment%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20federal%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20clutch%20of%20other%20senior%20veterans%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20politicisation%20of%20the%20services%20through%20government%20edicts.%20They%20said%20these%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Efirman%3C%2Fem%3Es%E2%80%99%20(decrees)%20were%20being%20employed%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98force%20multiplier%E2%80%99%20to%20favourably%20assist%20it%20electorally%2C%20much%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20service%20ethics%2C%20neutrality%20and%20above%20all%2C%20apolitical-ness.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20such%20government%20venture%20is%20Project%20Udbhav%20(genesis)%2C%20formally%20launched%20by%20defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20over%20the%20weekend%20to%20%E2%80%9Csynthesise%20ancient%20wisdom%20with%20contemporary%20military%20practices%20to%20forge%20a%20unique%20and%20holistic%20approach%20to%20address%20modern%20security%20challenges%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154551%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.45.15-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154551%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.45.15-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154551%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.45.15-PM-300x188.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25154551%2FScreenshot-2023-10-25-at-3.45.15-PM-1024x642.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681656%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22752%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20selfie%20point%20at%20Rajghat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20joint%20venture%20between%20the%20IA%20and%20the%20United%20Services%20Institution%20(USI)%20think%20tank%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Udbhav%20aims%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleseDetailm.aspx%3FPRID%3D1969684%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20Press%20Information%20Bureau%20(PIB)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20exploit%20India%E2%80%99s%205%2C000-year%20old%20civilisational%20legacy%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehend%20its%20enduring%20connect%2C%20relevance%20and%20applicability%20in%20the%20modern%20day%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20bequest%20includes%20studying%2C%20examining%20and%20analysing%20the%20writings%20of%20Chanakya%20(%3Cem%3EArthashastra%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20post-Mauryan%20Kamandaka%20(%3Cem%3ENitisara%3C%2Fem%3E)%20and%20those%20of%20the%20Tamil%20saint-poet%20Thiruvalluvar%20(%3Cem%3ETirukkural%3C%2Fem%3E)%2C%20all%20of%20which%20the%20PIB%20incredulously%20declared%20%E2%80%9C%5Balign%5D%20with%20modern%20military%20codes%20of%20ethics%20or%20just%20war%20and%20principles%20of%20the%20Geneva%20Convention%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20goes%20on%20to%20state%20that%20Udbhav%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cvisionary%20initiative%20by%20the%20%5BIA%5D%E2%80%9D%20seeking%20to%20%E2%80%9Cintegrate%20age-old%20wisdom%20with%20contemporary%20military%20pedagogy%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20enhancing%20%E2%80%9Cstrategic%20thinking%2C%20statecraft%20and%20warfare%E2%80%9D.%20In%20short%2C%20Udbhav%2C%20according%20to%20the%20MoD%20and%20the%20government%2C%20is%20poised%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfoster%20deeper%20understanding%E2%80%9D%20of%20military%20matters%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccontribute%20to%20enriching%20military%20curricula%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https