re%20schemes%20like%20the%20Swachh%20Bharat%20Abhiyan%20and%20Sarva%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan%20and%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20would%20be%20monitored%20by%20the%20soldiers%E2%80%99%20units%20through%20quarterly%20feedback%20supported%20by%20photographs%20and%20video%20clips.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20these%20%E2%80%98soldier%20ambassadors%E2%80%99%20have%20been%20asked%20by%20the%20IA%E2%80%99s%20Ceremonials%20and%20Welfare%20Directorate%20that%20functions%20under%20the%20adjutant%20general%E2%80%99s%20office%2C%20responsible%20for%20the%20forces%E2%80%99%20overall%20administration%2C%20to%20instruct%20their%20respective%20societies%20in%20patriotism%20and%20nationalism%2C%20hygiene%2C%20cleanliness%2C%20the%20perils%20of%20drug%20abuse%2C%20road%20safety%2C%20to%20motivate%20and%20mentor%20their%20youth%20and%20to%20organise%20sports%20events%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20military%20officials%20said%20that%20the%20Army%20Training%20Command%20in%20Shimla%20had%20issued%20formal%20guidelines%20for%20these%20soldiers%20to%20follow%20with%20regard%20to%20vindicating%20these%20%E2%80%98educative%E2%80%99%20tasks%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20%E2%80%98leveraging%E2%80%99%20their%20skills%20and%20innate%20discipline%20towards%20augmenting%20nation%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGeneral%20Panag%20estimates%20that%20at%20any%20given%20time%2C%20the%20armed%20forces%20will%20have%20some%20350%2C000%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20warriors%E2%80%9D%20engaged%20in%20various%20welfare%20activities%20at%20a%20time%2C%20in%20what%20he%20terms%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Farmy-cant-ask-soldiers-to-do-social-work-on-leave-its-beyond-the-call-of-duty%2F1750131%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Cbiggest%20government-led%20social%20service%20drive%20ever%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20soldiers%20are%20entitled%20to%20two%20months%20leave%20annually%2C%20in%20addition%20to%2030%20days%20of%20casual%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C