0Son%20Draws%20Fire%20For%20Staying%20In%20US%20Amid%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIsrael%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu's%20son%20Yair%20is%20drawing%20fire%20for%20remaining%20in%20the%20US%20at%20a%20time%20when%20nearly%204%20lakh%20youngsters%20from%20his%20country%20have%20joined%20the%20fight%20against%20Hamas%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20October%207%20attacks.%20The%20surprise%20attacks%20on%20Israel's%20cities%20left%20about%201%2C400%20dead%20and%20sparked%20a%20brutal%20retaliation%20that%20has%20killed%20over%205%2C000%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20Yair%20moved%20to%20Florida%20earlier%20this%20year.%20A%20photo%20of%20the%2032-year-old%20on%20a%20beach%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20with%20many%20claiming%20that%20he%20is%20enjoying%20in%20Miami%20while%20his%20countrymen%20fly%20home%20to%20join%20the%20fight%20against%20Hamas.%20NDTV%20cannot%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20photograph.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Times%20spoke%20to%20one%20of%20the%20volunteers%20stationed%20on%20Israel's%20northern%20front.%20%26quot%3BYair%20is%20enjoying%20his%20life%20at%20Miami%20Beach%20while%20I'm%20on%20the%20front%20lines.%20It's%20us%20who%20are%20leaving%20our%20work%2C%20our%20families%2C%20our%20kids%2C%20to%20protect%20our%20families%20back%20home%20and%20the%20country%2C%20not%20the%20people%20who%20are%20responsible%20for%20this%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20soldier%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20soldier%20serving%20on%20the%20border%20with%20Gaza%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20flown%20back%20from%20the%20States%20where%20I%20have%20a%20job%2C%20a%20life%2C%20my%20family.%20There%20is%20no%20way%20I%20can%20stay%20there%20and%20abandon%20my%20country%2C%20my%20people%2C%20at%20this%20critical%20time.%20Where%20is%20the%20prime%20minister's%20son%3F%20Why%20isn't%20he%20in%20Israel%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20most%20uniting%20moment%20for%20