dia's%20Young%20Minds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20nation%20that%20adds%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20vulnerable%20young%20minds%20to%20platforms%20like%20Instagram%2C%20Meta's%20insidious%20tactics%20are%20not%20just%20a%20far-off%20Silicon%20Valley%20problem%3B%20they%20are%20a%20ticking%20time%20bomb%20in%20our%20own%20homes.%20Yet%2C%20the%20irony%20is%20that%20India%20is%20among%20the%20last%20to%20raise%20a%20flag%20against%20the%20digital%20colonisation%20of%20its%20young%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Meta%2C%20which%20owns%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%2C%20was%20sued%20by%20more%20than%20three%20dozen%20US%20states%20for%20knowingly%20using%20features%20to%20hook%20children%20to%20its%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20where%20the%20concept%20of%20%26quot%3Bfamily%26quot%3B%20is%20sacrosanct%2C%20where%20elders%20are%20revered%2C%20and%20children%20are%20considered%20divine%20gifts%2C%20it's%20a%20paradox%20that%20we've%20allowed%20a%20platform%20to%20infiltrate%20our%20homes%20and%20minds%20so%20insidiously.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERemember%20the%20fervour%20with%20which%20activists%20and%20social%20crusaders%20took%20to%20the%20streets%2C%20holding%20%3Cem%3Edharnas%3C%2Fem%3E%20against%20Meta%20for%20Net%20Neutrality%3F%20The%20issue%20became%20a%20rallying%20cry%2C%20a%20cause%20that%20united%20people%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life.%20So%2C%20why%20the%20deafening%20silence%20now%3F%20Do%20we%20consider%20our%20children's%20emotional%20and%20psychological%20well-being%20%26quot%3Bsoft%26quot%3B%20issues%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Quiet%20Desperation%20of%20Sameera%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20weeks%20ago%2C%20I%20met%20Sameera%2C%20an%2011-year-old%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20who%20seemed%20quieter%20than%20her%20usual%20%26quot%3Bbubbly%26quot%3B%20self.%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20going%20on%2C%20Sameera%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked%20(name%20changed%20to%20protect%20her%20identity).%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20hates%20me!%26quot%3B%20came%20her%20swift%20reply.%20She%20didn't%20say%20much%20more%2C%20but%20her%20eyes%20spoke%20volumes.%20I%20couldn't%20shake%20the%20feeling%20that%20something%20inside%20her%20was%20breaking%2C%20crumbling%20into%20pieces%20too%20small%20to%20put%20back%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%20in%20Bengaluru%20told%20me%20that%20children's%20emotional%20resilience%20is%20becoming%20%26quot%3Bwafer-thin%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20touchy%20world%20of%20Instagram.%20Sometimes%2C%20we%20also%20find%20suicidal%20tendencies%2C%20rarely%2C%20but%20it's%20there.%26quot%3B%20It%20made%20me%20wonder%20about%20my%2012-year-old%20daughter%2C%20her%20friends%2C%20and%20my%20nieces.%20The%20danger%20lurks%20around%20us%2C%20and%20finding%20Instagram%20accounts%20for%209%20to%2012-year-olds%20is%20mainstream.%20It's%20fashionable%2C%20existential%2C%20and%20a%20necessity%20they%20can't%20live%20without.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Poison%20We%20Feed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20see%20it%2C%20don't%20we%3F%20The%20anxiety%2C%20the%20depression%2C%20and%20the%20emotional%20turmoil%20these%20platforms%20are%20causing%20our%20children.%20Yet%2C%20we%20often%20look%20away%2C%20handing%20mobile%20screens%20to%20young%20ones%20to%20keep%20them%20engrossed%20and%20out%20of%20our%20hair.%20We're%20inculcating%20a%20poisonous%20habit%20from%20early%20childhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20Instagram%20Reaches%20India's%20Heartland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20I%20was%20in%20Dhakjari%2C%20a%20nondescript%20village%20in%20Bihar's%20Madhubani%20district.%20I%20was%20there%20on%20assignment%20for%20another%20story%2C%20but%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20I%20know%20that%20stories%20often%20find%20you%20when%20you%20least%20expect%20them.%20That's%20how%20I%20met%20Rani%2C%20a%2010-year-old%20girl%20who%20was%20as%20engrossed%20in%20her%20father's%20smartphone%20as%20any%20child%20in%20an%20upscale%20Mumbai%20or%20Delhi%20neighbourhood%20might%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20looking%20at%2C%20Rani%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked%2C%20curious.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Faisu%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20replied%20without%20moving%20her%20gaze%20from%20the%20screen.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20really%20cool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20uninitiated%2C%20Mr.%20Faisu%20is%20an%20Instagram%20influencer%20with%20millions%20of%20followers.%20Rani%20went%20on%20to%20tell%20me%20how%20her%20elder%20siblings%20had%20been%20hooked%20on%20TikTok%20until%20it%20was%20banned%20in%20India.%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20watch%20them%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20her%20eyes%20finally%20meeting%20mine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20struck%20me%20that%20Rani%20was%20consuming%20the%20same%20digital%20content%20as%20her%20urban%20counterparts%20and%20it%20was%20taking%20an%20emotional%20toll%20on%20her.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20the%20phone%20is%20snatched%20away%20from%20her%2C%20she%20goes%20into%20oblivion%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20elder%20brother%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20Early%20Warning%20Ignored%3A%20The%20Calculated%20Indifference%20of%20Meta%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20Facebook%20-%20now%20Meta%20-%20announced%20it%20was%20pausing%20the%20development%20of%20an%20Instagram%20service%20tailored%20for%20children%20who%20are%2013%20or%20younger.%20This%20was%20a%20reluctant%20step%20back%20in%20the%20face%20of%20mounting%20criticism.%20The%20company's%20internal%20research%2C%20reported%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20showed%20Instagram's%20detrimental%20mental%20health%20effects%20on%20teenage%20girls.%20Yet%2C%20Meta%20still%20wanted%20to%20build%20an%20Instagram%20product%20for%20children%2C%20promising%20a%20more%20%26quot%3Bage-appropriate%20experience%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20halt%20the%20app's%20development%20is%20a%20rare%20reversal%20for%20Meta%2C%20which%20has%20become%20perhaps%20the%20world's%20most%20heavily%20scrutinised%20corporation.%20The%20company's%20statement%20that%20it%20would%20take%20time%20to%20%26quot%3Bwork%20with%20parents%2C%20experts%2C%20policymakers%2C%20and%20regulators%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20smokescreen.%20It's%20a%20calculated%20move%20to%20buy%20time%20and%20wait%20for%20the%20public%20outcry%20to%20simmer%20down%20so%20they%20can%20proceed%20with%20their%20plans%20unobstructed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeta%20argued%20that%20young%20people%20were%20using%20the%20photo-sharing%20app%20anyway%2C%20despite%20age-requirement%20rules%2C%20so%20it%20would%20be%20better%20to%20develop%20a%20more%20suitable%20version.%20This%20is%20akin%20to%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BKids%20are%20going%20to%20smoke%20anyway%2C%20so%20let's%20give%20them%20'light'%20cigarettes.%26quot%3B%20It's%20a%20flawed%2C%20dangerous%20logic%20that%20underscores%20Meta's%20ultimate%20motive%3A%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20internal%20research%20showed%20that%20Instagram%20had%20caused%20teen%20girls%20to%20feel%20worse%20about%20their%20bodies%20and%20had%20led%20to%20increased%20rates%20of%20anxiety%20and%20depression.%20And%20yet%2C%20they%20were%20planning%20to%20target%20an%20even%20younger%20demographic.%20This%20is%20predatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20a%20report%20titled%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rsph.org.uk%2Four-work%2Fcampaigns%2Fstatus-of-mind.html%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BStatus%20of%20Mind%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20flagged%20how%2091%20per%20cent%20of%20people%20between%2016%20and%2024%20were%20using%20the%20internet%20for%20social%20networking%20and%20that%20rates%20of%20anxiety%20and%20depression%20had%20risen%2070%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20past%2025%20years.%20The%20report%20called%20for%20actions%20like%20pop-up%20heavy%20usage%20warnings%20and%20teaching%20safe%20social%20media%20use%20in%20schools.%20Four%20years%20later%2C%20Meta%20is%20sued%20for%20knowingly%20hooking%20children%20to%20its%20platforms.%20The%20early%20signs%20were%20there%20-%20we%20chose%20to%20ignore%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Digital%20Pied%20Pipers%20of%20India's%20Young%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe've%20unleashed%20a%20Pandora's%20box%20in%20a%20country%20where%20digital%20literacy%20campaigns%20have%20been%20hailed%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20progress.%20Children%2C%20barely%20in%20their%20teens%2C%20are%20now%20armed%20with%20smartphones%2C%20scrolling%20through%20an%20endless%20feed%20of%20filtered%20realities.%20They%20are%20learning%2C%20but%20what%20exactly%20are%20they%20learning%3F%20To%20equate%20self-worth%20with%20likes%3F%20To%20seek%20validation%20from%20strangers%20in%20distant%20lands%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20let's%20not%20forget%20the%20influencers%2C%20the%20new-age%20Pied%20Pipers%2C%20leading%20this%20vulnerable%20demographic%20down%20a%20path%20fraught%20with%20mental%20health%20risks.%20They%20post%20glamorous%20photos%2C%20flaunting%20lifestyles%20that%20are%20often%20unattainable%2C%20creating%20a%20mirage%20that%20many%20in%20these%20small%20towns%20and%20villages%20chase%2C%20unaware%20of%20the%20mental%20health%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20are%20we%20not%20questioning%20these%20influencers%2C%20who%20profit%20from%20the%20insecurities%20they%20help%20instil%3F%20They%2C%20too%2C%20are%20part%20of%20this%20%26quot%3Bexploitation%20ecosystem%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20it's%20high%20time%20we%20held%20them%20accountable.%20They%20are%20not%20just%20influencing%20fashion%20choices%20or%20vacation%20spots%3B%20they%20are%20shaping%20self-esteem%2C%20moulding%20perceptions%20of%20success%20and%20failure%2C%20and%20doing%20it%20from%20the%20bustling%20cities%20to%20the%20remotest%20corners%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Uncomfortable%20Mirror%3A%20What%20Sameera's%20Silence%20Tells%20Us%20All%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20circle%20back%20to%20my%20conversation%20with%20Sameera%2C%20the%2011-year-old%20who%20felt%20the%20world%20was%20against%20her%2C%20and%20the%20psychiatrist%20who%20warned%20of%20children's%20%26quot%3Bwafer-thin%20emotional%20resilience%26quot%3B%2C%20I%20can't%20help%20but%20think%20of%20Rani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERani's%20story%20is%20a%20haunting%20echo%20of%20Sameera's.%20Both%20are%20young%20girls%2C%20separated%20by%20geography%20but%20united%20by%20the%20invisible%20threads%20of%20social%20media%20weaving%20a%20web%20of%20complex%20emotional%20and%20psychological%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20difference%20between%20Rani%20and%20a%20child%20in%20an%20urban%20setting%20isn't%20the%20content%20they%20consume%3B%20it's%20the%20context%20in%20which%20they%20consume%20it.%20In%20a%20village%20like%20Dhakjari%2C%20where%20even%20basic%20amenities%20can%20be%20a%20luxury%2C%20the%20aspirational%20lifestyles%20peddled%20by%20influencers%20are%20not%20just%20unattainable%3B%20they%20are%20cruel%20fiction.%20Yet%2C%20the%20emotional%20dependencies%20-%20the%20highs%20of%20a%20'like'%20and%20the%20lows%20of%20its%20absence%20-%20are%20universal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20handed%20our%20children%20the%20keys%20to%20a%20digital%20kingdom%20that%20we%20don't%20fully%20understand%2C%20governed%20by%20algorithms%20designed%20to%20exploit%20their%20vulnerabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20don't%20act%20now%2C%20if%20we%20don't%20force%20policymakers%20and%20corporations%20to%20change%2C%20then%20we're%20failing%20Sameera%20and%20Rani%20and%20an%20entire%20generation.%20So%2C%20parents%2C%20scrutinise%20the%20digital%20diets%20you're%20feeding%20your%20children.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolicymakers%2C%20it's%20high%20time%20you%20legislate%20for%20the%20emotional%20well-being%20of%20our%20children.%20And%2C%20to%20the%20young%20minds%20caught%20in%20this%20digital%20web%2C%20remember%20-%20your%20worth%20is%20not%20measured%20in%20likes%20or%20follows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt's%20time%20to%20reclaim%20our