C%20said%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Rutu%20Raba.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20seven%20accused%20involved%20in%20the%20murder%20of%20Odedara%20were%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Raba%2C%20adding%20that%20further%20investigation%20is%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20included%20Raja%20Kuchhadia%2C%20Raju%20Keshwala%2C%20Ramde%20Bokhiria%2C%20Pratik%20Gorania%20and%20three%20of%20their%20accomplices.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%2C%20these%20accused%20had%20organised%20an%20event%20related%20to%20garba%2C%20a%20traditional%20dance%2C%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20Navratri%20near%20a%20school%20adjacent%20to%20Krishna%20Park%2C%20where%20the%20Odedara%20family%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20complaint%20to%20Udhyognagar%20police%20in%20Porbandar%2C%20Odedara's%20wife%20Maliben%20said%20she%20went%20to%20confront%20the%20organisers%20on%20Monday%20night%20when%20their%2011-year-old%20daughter%20came%20home%20after%20playing%20garba%20and%20complained%20that%20though%20she%20had%20won%20two%20different%20events%2C%20she%20was%20given%20only%20one%20prize%20by%20the%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Maliben%20went%20to%20the%20organisers%20with%20her%20daughter's%20complaint%2C%20Keshwala%20apparently%20rudely%20told%20her%20to%20accept%20the%20decision.%20Take%20the%20prize%20or%20leave%20it%2C%20she%20was%20told%2C%20says%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20Kuchhadia%20and%20Bokhiria%20also%20arrived%20at%20the%20spot%20and%20allegedly%20started%20arguing%20with%20Maliben.%20They%20even%20threatened%20to%20kill%20her%20if%20she%20did%20not%20leave%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20FIR%2C%20the%20wives%20of%20Kuchhadia%20and%20Keshwala%20also%20verbally%20abused%20Maliben%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20leave%20the%20place.%20Maliben%20and%20her%20daughter%20then%20went%20back%20home%20around%201%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20hour%2C%20when%20Maliben%20and%20her%20husband%20were%20sitting%20outside%20their%20house%2C%20the%20four%20main%20accused%20and%20three%20of%20their%20accomplices%20came%20there%20on%20motorcycles%20and%20started%20beating%20Odedara%20using%20sticks%20and%20wooden%20planks%2C%20according%20to%20the%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaliben%20also%20received%20injuries%20when%20she%20tried%20to%20save%20her%20husband.%20The%20accused%20then%20took%20Odedara%20to%20the%20garba%20venue%20on%20their%20bikes%20and%20thrashed%20him%20till%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20police%2C%20who%20were%20alerted%20by%20the%20victim's%20minor%20daughter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOdedara%20was%20rushed%20to%20a%20hospital%20by%20the%20police%20in%20their%20vehicle%2C%20but%20he%20could%20not%20be%20saved%2C%20the%20FIR%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698220260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fr53uhru8_garba-ani_625x300_22_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-beaten-to-death-with-sticks-after-fight-over-garba-prize-in-gujarat-4511532%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2040-year-old%20man%20was%20bludgeoned%20to%20death%20allegedly%20by%20the%20organisers%20of%20a%20'garba'%20function%20in%20Gujarat%20after%20he%20had%20a%20spat%20with%20them%20following%20his%2011-year-old%20daughter's%20complaint%20that%20she%20was%20given%20one%20prize%20despite%20winning%20two%20events%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-beaten-to-death-with-sticks-after-fight-over-garba-prize-in-gujarat-4511532%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fman-beaten-to-death-with-sticks-after-fight-over-garba-prize-in-gujarat-