rl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fapec-summit-san-francisco-targets-hot-dog-stands-homeless-people%2Famp_articleshow%2F104691856.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Man%20Sues%20US%20Airline%20After%20Crew%20Spills%20Hot%20Coffee%20On%20Him%2C%20Damages%20His%20Tattoo%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20from%20the%20United%20States%20has%20sued%20American%20Airlines%20after%20a%20flight%20attendant%20spilled%20hot%20coffee%20on%20him%20which%20left%20him%20%26quot%3Bscalded%26quot%3B.%20The%20incident%20took%20place%20on%20October%209%20on%20a%20flight%20from%20Vietnam%20to%20New%20York%2C%20which%20left%20George%20Latorre%20with%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20and%20permanent%20injuries%26quot%3B%20that%20caused%20damage%20to%20his%20tattoo%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2023%2F10%2F24%2Fbusiness%2Famerican-airlines-passengers-tattoo-damaged-after-it-was-scalded%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20filed%20a%20suit%20against%20the%20airline%20and%20said%20that%20a%20crew%20member%20spilled%20hot%20coffee%20on%20his%20left%20arm%20which%20caused%20%26quot%3Bsecond%20degree%20(burns)%20to%20his%20upper%20left%20arm%3B%20blistering%3B%20peeling%2C%20bleeding%3B%20possible%20permanent%20cosmetic%20deformity%20and%20scarring.%26quot%3B%20The%20man%20was%20sitting%20in%20seat%2033J%20next%20to%20his%20son%20when%20the%20incident%20took%20place.%20When%20the%20flight%20attendant%20served%20him%20coffee%2C%20it%20spilled%20on%20him.%20According%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20the%20staff%20member%20was%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Bcareless%2C%20reckless%2C%20and%20negligent%20in%20serving%20scalding%20coffee%20to%20the%20plaintiff%20in%20an%20unsafe%20manner.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20that%20the%20injuries%20have%20resulted%20in%20%26quot%3Bextreme%20pain%20and%20suffering%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bemotional%20harm%2C%20mental%20anguish%20and%20distress.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20he%20has%20also%20suffered%20from%20%26quot%3Bloss%20of%20sleep%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20discomfort%2C%20which%20will%20require%20more%20medical%20care.%20The%20lawsuit%20states%20that%20the%20airline%20is%20at%20fault%20for%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Bfailing%20to%20hire%20and%20retain%20competent%20personnel%20and%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20%26quot%3Bburned%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20coffee%2C%20Mr%20Latorre%20attempted%20to%20purchase%20a%20business%20class%20seat%20from%20the%20airline%2C%20but%20the%20lawsuit%20claimed%20that%20he%20was%20turned%20down.%20He%20then%20sought%20medical%20assistance%20for%20his%20injuries%20after%20landing.%20A%20medical%20professional%20then%20informed%20him%20that%20the%20damage%20was%20%26quot%3Bserious%20enough%26quot%3B%20to%20need%20a%20surgeon's%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20American%20Airlines%20representative%20spoke%20to%20the%20outlet%20and%20said%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bdoes%20not%20comment%20on%20pending%20litigation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20this%20year%2C%20in%20a%20similar%20case%2C%20a%20Florida%20family%20was%20awarded%20%24800%2C000%2C%20following%20a%20civil%20lawsuit%20against%20McDonald's%20and%20a%20franchisee.%20The%20South%20Florida%20jury%20delivered%20the%20verdict%20after%20a%204-year-old%20girl%20named%20Olivia%20Caraballo%2C%20suffered%20second-degree%20burns%20from%20a%20McDonald's%20chicken%20nugget%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fflorida-girl-burned-mcdonalds-chicken-mcnugget-awarded-800000-damages-olivia-caraballo%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECBS%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELawyers%20for%20the%20family%20were%20seeking%20%2415%20million%20in%20damages.%20However%2C%20jurors%20reached%20their%20verdict%20after%20deliberating%20for%20less%20than%20two%20hours.%20After%20he