20latest%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20coming%20three%20decades%2C%20India%20will%20see%20the%20largest%20energy%20demand%20growth%20of%20any%20country%20or%20region%20in%20the%20world%2C%20PTI%20cited%20IEA%E2%80%99s%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iea.org%2Freports%2Fworld-energy-outlook-2023%5C%22%3EWorld%20Energy%20Outlook%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20projections%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20energy%20supply%20is%20set%20to%20rise%20from%2042%20exajoules%20(EJ)%20in%202022%20to%2053.7%20EJ%20in%202030%2C%20and%2073%20EJ%20in%202050%20under%20its%20stated%20policy%20scenarios.%20It%20would%20touch%2047.6%20EJ%20by%202030%20and%2060.3%20EJ%20by%202050%20as%20per%20announced%20pledges.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20witnessed%2C%20according%20to%20IEA%2C%20700%20heatwave%20events%20in%20the%20last%20five%20decades%2C%20which%20led%20to%2017%2C000%20deaths.%20Therefore%2C%20air%20conditioner%20ownership%20in%20India%20would%20go%20up%20massively%20in%20the%20coming%20decades%20with%20rising%20incomes.%20Geographical%20and%20meteorological%20conditions%20would%20also%20contribute%20to%20this%20spike.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20number%20of%20air%20conditioners%20since%202010%20has%20tripled%2C%20to%20reach%2024%20units%20per%20100%20households.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20impact%20of%20cooling%20needs%20on%20electricity%20consumption%20is%20already%20clear.%20Electricity%20demand%20is%20sensitive%20to%20temperatures%2C%20and%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20there%20is%20a%20sharp%20increase%20in%20demand%20as%20temperatures%20cross%20the%2025-degree%20Celsius%20threshold%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20IEA%20in%20its%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EContinuing%20further%2C%20it%20said%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CHousehold%20air%20conditioner%20ownership%20is%20estimated%20to%20expand%20ninefold%20by%202050%20across%20the%20IEA%20scenarios%2C%20outpacing%20the%20growth%20in%20ownership%20of%20every%20other%20major%20household%20appliance%20including%20televisions%2C%20refrigerators%2C%20and%20washing%20machines.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IEA%20report%20also%20said%20India%20is%20moving%20towards%20a%20dynamic%20new%20phase%20as%20part%20of%20its%20energy%20development%20marked%20by%20a%20long-term%20net%20zero%20emissions%20ambition%2C%20increased%20regulatory%20sophistication%2C%20a%20focus%20on%20clean%20energy%20deployment%2C%20and%20the%20creation%20of%20domestic%20clean%20energy%20technology%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20oil%20is%20estimated%20to%20go%20up%20from%205.2%20million%20barrels%20per%20day%20(bpd)%20in%202022%20to%206.8%20million%20bpd%20in%202030%20and%207.8%20million%20bpd%20in%202050%20under%20the%20stated%20policy%20scenario.%20As%20per%20announced%20pledges%2C%20the%20demand%20would%20shoot%20up%20to%206.2%20million%20bpd%20in%202030%20and%204.7%20million%20bpd%20in%202050.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698211836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F28092610%2FPower_lines_8618709561.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Findia-to-witness-largest-energy-demand-globally-by-2050-power-for-acs-to-spike-nine-fold-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20latest%20'World%20Energy%20Outlook'%20report%20by%20International%20Energy%20Agency%2C%20the%20total%20power%20consumption%20in%20India%20in%20the%20next%20three%20decades%20would%20exceed%20whole%20of%20Africa%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenergy%2Findia-to-witness-largest-energy-demand-globally-by-2050-power-for-acs-to-spike-nine-fold-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Catastrophic'%20hurricane%20hits%20Mexican%20beach%20resort%20town%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698211680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.co