h%2C%20their%20ethnicity%2C%20their%20nationality%20or%20any%20other%20reason%2C%26quot%3B%20Blinken%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20stressed%20that%20the%20Security%20Council%20has%20a%20responsibility%20to%20denounce%20member%20states%20that%20arm%2C%20fund%20and%20train%20Hamas%20or%20%26quot%3Bany%20other%20terrorist%20group%20that%20carries%20out%20such%20horrific%20acts.%26quot%3B%20Blinken's%20remarks%20appeared%20to%20make%20a%20reference%20to%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20carried%20out%20by%20Pakistan-based%20terrorist%20organisation%20Lashkar-e-Taiba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698207960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F6jl8i3qg_r-ravindra_625x300_25_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-treat-with-contempt-india-on-pakistans-kashmir-reference-at-un-4511054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20said%20it%20will%20treat%20a%20reference%20by%20Pakistan%20to%20Kashmir%20during%20a%20Security%20Council%20meeting%20on%20the%20Israel-Gaza%20situation%20with%20the%20contempt%20it%20deserves%20and%20will%20not%20dignify%20it%20with%20a%20response.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-treat-with-contempt-india-on-pakistans-kashmir-reference-at-un-4511054%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-treat-with-contempt-india-on-pakistans-kashmir-reference-at-un-4511054%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-treat-with-contempt-india-on-pakistans-kashmir-reference-at-un-4511054%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hamas%20fighter%20boasts%20of%20killing%20Jews%20in%20chilling%20phone%20cal