%20battles%20off%20the%20field%20besides%20deceiving%20batsmen%20with%20his%20flight%20and%20guile%20on%20the%20pitch.%20He%20never%20hesitated%20to%20speak%20his%20mind%20on%20contentious%20issues%20concerning%20the%20sport%2C%20like%20chucking%20and%20match-fixing.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20was%20that%20Bedi%20had%20a%20large%20heart%2C%20was%20compassionate%20and%20went%20out%20of%20his%20way%20to%20help%20other%20cricketers.%20For%20example%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20charge%20those%20who%20came%20from%20afar%20to%20train%20at%20his%20cricket%20school%20in%20Delhi%20and%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20pay%20the%20fee.%20Some%20people%20who%20benefitted%20from%20his%20assistance%20might%20admit%20the%20help%20he%20extended%20to%20them%2C%20but%20others%20may%20not.%20Bedi%20himself%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20world%20to%20know%20%E2%80%93%20he%20helped%20them%20because%20of%20the%20goodness%20of%20his%20heart%2C%20not%20for%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20when%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20left-arm%20spinner%20Saurabh%20Kumar%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20the%20fee%20at%20Bedi%20Paaji%E2%80%99s%20coaching%20centre%2C%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20charge%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20former%20test%20batsman%20Gursharan%20Singh%2C%20who%20captained%20the%20Bedi-coached%20Punjab%20team%20to%20their%20epochal%20Ranji%20Trophy%20triumph%20in%201992-93%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20prominent%20former%20India%20Test%20batsman%2C%20who%20was%20close%20to%20Bedi%2C%20passed%20away%20many%20years%20ago%2C%20he%20collected%20money%20to%20help%20the%20cricketer%E2%80%99s%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGursharan%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20teams%20that%20toured%20New%20Zealand%20and%20the%20West%20Indies%20in%20early%201989-90%2C%20when%20Bedi%20was%20coach.%20Although%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20stint%20didn%E2%80%99t%20last%20long%2C%20one%20high%20point%20of%20his%20tenure%20was%20that%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20scored%20his%20maiden%20Test%20century%20under%20his%20watch%2C%20in%201990%20in%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Tendulkar%20paid%20a%20touching%20tribute%20to%20Bedi%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%3A%20%E2%80%9CSashu%2C%20he%E2%80%99d%20say%20with%20warmth%20that%20only%20he%20possessed.%20To%20Bishan%20Paaji%2C%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20another%20cricketer%3B%20I%20was%20like%20a%20son.%20Under%20his%20nurturing%20guidance%2C%20I%20scored%20my%20first%20100%20in%20England.%20On%20chilly%20NZ%20evenings%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20sit%20over%20meals%2C%20and%20I%E2%80%99d%20hang%20on%20to%20every%20story%20he%20told%2C%20every%20piece%20of%20wisdom%20he%20shared.%20Today%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20echoing%20silence%20where%20his%20voice%20used%20to%20be.%20The%20world%20seems%20a%20little%20emptier%20without%20you%2C%20Paaji.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fplayer-power-over-personal-success-bishan-singh-bedis-true-impact-on-indian-cricket%5C%22%3EPlayer%20Power%20Over%20Personal%20Success%3A%20Bishan%20Singh%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20True%20Impact%20on%20Indian%20Cricket%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20is%20poorer%20without%20the%20colourful%20Bedi.%20Not%20just%20Indians%2C%20but%20his%20contemporaries%20like%20former%20Pakistan%20captain%20Intikhab%20Alam%20and%20West%20Indies%20fast%20bowling%20legend%20Michael%20Holding%20paid%20rich%20tributes%20to%20the%20genial%20Sikh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20a%20magician%20with%20the%20ball%20but%20besides%20that%2C%20he%20was%20a%20great%20human%20being.%20I%20have%20never%20seen%20anyone%20as%20genuine%20as%20Bishan.%20There%20was%20no%20fakeness%20in%20him.%20He%20was%20the%20same%20inside%20out.%20I%20used%20to%20get%20worried%20because%20of%20his%20personality.%20Whenever%20I%20used%20to%20warn%20him%2C%20%E2%80%98Bishan%2C%20sometimes%20it%20is%20okay%20to%20be%20diplomatic.%E2%80%99%20In%20his%20younger%20days%2C%20he%20would%20reply%2C%20%E2%80%98I%20will%20try.%E2%80%99%20After%20his%20retirement%2C%20he%20would%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98ab%20toh%20aadat%20daal%20lo%20(At%20least%20get%20used%20to%20it%20now)%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20wrote%20Alam%20in%20a%20first-person%20account%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-passes-away-lost-a-younger-brother-lost-a-part-of-my-heart-mourns-pakistans-intikhab-alam-8996225%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20indeed%20a%20sad%20day%20for%20world%20cricket.%20We%20have%20lost%20a%20gem.%20Our%20friendship%20will%20continue%20till%20the%20time%20I%20am%20alive.%20He%20loved%20me%20like%20his%20elder%20brother.%20I%20loved%20him%20like%20my%20younger%20brother.%20I%20may%20never%20sing%20Louis%20Armstrong%E2%80%99s%20songs.%20Maybe%2C%20once%20we%20meet%20in%20another%20life.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHolding%2C%20too%2C%20poured%20genuine%20praise%20on%20Bedi.%20%E2%80%9CBishan%20was%20the%20greatest%20moral%20voice%20of%20Indian%20cricket.%20Bish%20liked%20to%20be%20morally%20right%3B%20not%20popularly%20right.%20He%20was%20never%20afraid%20of%20giving%20opinions%3B%20it%20was%20his%20opinion%20and%20he%20said%20it%20the%20way%20he%20saw%20it.%20I%20like%20that%20about%20people%20and%20like%20to%20think%20I%20am%20similar%20to%20him%20in%20that%20vein.%20He%20never%20looked%20to%20get%20something%20out%20of%20the%20game%20by%20any%20means.%20A%20man%20of%20morals%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20care%20if%20his%20views%20weren%E2%80%99t%20popular%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-was-indian-crickets-greatest-moral-voice-michael-holding-offers-his-tribute-8996621%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20is%20one%20of%20the%20great%20romantics%20of%20the%20game%3B%20he%20genuinely%20loved%20the%20sport%20and%20was%20wary%20about%20the%20negative%20tentacles%20spreading%20around%20it.%20He%20was%20morally%20against%20all%20things%20that%20were%20bad.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20way%20you%20need%20to%20be.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20be%20afraid%20to%20speak%20out.%20He%20never%20was.%20The%20secret%20to%20that%20confidence%20is%20he%20knew%20he%20was%20speaking%20the%20truth%20to%20the%20power.%20Truth%20is%20something%20to%20never%20be%20afraid%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMukul%20Mudgal%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%20and%20a%20cricket%20follower%2C%20also%20has%20fond%20memories%20of%20watching%20Bedi%20display%20his%20art.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20most%20abiding%20memory%20of%20Bedi%20is%20Australian%20Doug%20Walters%20(the%20best%20batsman%20of%20his%20time)%20facing%20him%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Test%20against%20Bill%20Lawrry-led%20Australia.%20Walters%20shouldered%20arms%2C%20anticipating%20turn%2C%20but%20the%20ball%20came%20in%20with%20the%20arm%20and%20bowled%20him.%20A%20thoroughly%20bewildered%20Walters%20walked%20back%20shaking%20his%20head%20in%20disbelief.%20Subtle%20in%20his%20flight%20and%20turn%2C%20Bedi%20was%20equally%20forthright%20in%20his%20criticism%20of%20the%20cricket%20establishment%20and%20in%20particular%20the%20Delhi%20and%20District%20Cricket%20Association%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYashovardhan%20Azad%2C%20a%20former%20top%20cop%20who%20accompanied%20the%20Indian%20team%20as%20security%20liaison%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20historic%20tour%20of%20Pakistan%20in%202004%2C%20said%20the%20Feroze%20Shah%20Kotla%20grounds%20in%20Delhi%2C%20home%20to%20Bedi%20for%20years%2C%20should%20be%20named%20after%20him.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20one%20after%20whom%20the%20Kotla%20stadium%20shd%20be%20named%20it%20is%20Bishan%20Bedi.%20True%20leader%2C%20spin%20wizard%20led%20Delhi%20%26amp%3B%20country%20to%20glory.%20Till%20end%20crusader%20against%20the%20corrupt%20in%20Delhi%20%26amp%3B%20India%20cricket.%20Will%20always%20miss%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyashoazad%2Fstatus%2F1716420715417612750%5C%22%3Etweeted%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBedi%20was%20never%20the%20same%20after%20he%20underwent%20successive%20operations%2C%20including%20an%20open%20heart%20surgery%2C%20in%20February%202021.%20He%20became%20quiet%20and%20was%20confined%20largely%20to%20the%20wheelchair.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23233659%2FThe-Wire-52.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23233659%2FThe-Wire-52.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23233659%2FThe-Wire-52-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23233659%2FThe-Wire-52-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681456%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EBishan%20Singh%20Bedi.%20Photo%3A%20Screengrab%20via%20YouTube%20video%2FCricket%20Hall%20of%20Fame.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmritsar%20to%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBedi%2C%20born%20in%20Amritsar%2C%20represented%20the%20erstwhile%20Northern%20Punjab%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20national%20championship%20from%201961-62%20to%201966-67%2C%20before%20switching%20to%20Delhi%20(1968-69%20to%201980-81).%20So%2C%20Bedi%20bagged%20many%20of%20his%201%2C560%20first-class%20wickets%20for%20Delhi.%20He%20settled%20in%20Delhi%20for%20good%20and%20purchased%20a%20sprawling%20farmhouse%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20where%20he%20also%20had%20pet%20dogs%20and%20peacocks%20for%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBedi%20went%20on%20to%20lead%20Delhi%20and%20guided%20the%20team%20to%20its%20first-ever%20Ranji%20Trophy%20final%20in%201976-77.%20But%20Delhi%20on%20their%20home%20ground%20lost%20to%20the%20Sunil%20Gavaskar-led%20Bombay.%20After%20a%20year%2C%20Bedi%20captained%20Delhi%20to%20their%20first%20title%2C%20in%201978-79%2C%20and%20repeated%20the%20feat%20the%20next%20season.%20Delhi%20entered%20their%20third%20straight%20final%20in%201980-81%2C%20but%20this%20time%20Eknath%20Solkar%E2%80%99s%20Bombay%2C%20playing%20on%20their%20home%20ground%2C%20defeated%20Delhi.%20This%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20last%20Ranji%20Trophy%20and%20first-class%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBedi%20had%20transformed%20Delhi%20into%20a%20force%20to%20be%20reckoned%20with.%20In%20all%2C%20Delhi%20entered%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%2012%20times%20in%2016%20seasons%20(from%201976-77%20to%201991-92)%20and%20won%20the%20crown%20six%20times%2C%20under%20his%20guidance%20and%20after%20his%20departure.%20To%20date%2C%20this%20is%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20best%20period%20in%20the%20national%20championship.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbishan-singh-bedi-bowled-to-deceive-but-frank-and-big-hearted-was-the-least-deceptive-of-men%5C%22%3EBishan%20Singh%20Bedi%20Bowled%20to%20Deceive%20but%2C%20Frank%20and%20Big-Hearted%2C%20Was%20the%20Least%20Deceptive%20of%20Men%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransforming%20Punjab%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20after%20he%20stopped%20playing%20competitive%20cricket%2C%20Bedi%20joined%20the%20Punjab%20team%20as%20coach%20in%20the%20mid-1980s.%20He%20transformed%20the%20team%20completely%20%E2%80%93%20much%20like%20he%20had%20Delhi%20as%20captain%20%E2%80%93%20and%20guided%20them%20to%20their%20first-ever%20Ranji%20Trophy%20title%20in%20a%20dream%20campaign%20in%201992-93.%20Gursharan%20Singh%2C%20the%20batsman%20who%20had%20impressed%20Bedi%20as%20a%20teenager%2C%20was%20captain.%20It%20was%20at%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20request%20that%20he%20switched%20sides%20from%20Delhi%20to%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGursharan%20gives%20a%20lot%20of%20credit%20to%20Bedi%E2%80%99s%20insistence%20on%20physical%20fitness.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20was%20always%20a%20hard%20taskmaster.%20Before%20the%201992-93%20season%20started%2C%20Paaji%20organised%20a%20month-long%20preparatory%20camp%20at%20the%20Lakshmibai%20National%20Institute%20of%20Physical%20Education%20in%20Gwalior.%20We%20slogged%20it%20out%20for%20seven-eight%20hours%20daily%2C%20doing%20physical%20fitness%20in%20the%20mornings%20and%20working%20on%20our%20skills%20in%20the%20afternoons.%20This%20camp%20helped%20us%20a%20lot%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20during%20the%20tournament%2C%20Bedi%20made%20bold%20decisions%20that%20surprised%20some%20people.%20He%20gave%20batsman%20Amit%20Sharma%20the%20big%20break%20in%20the%20crucial%20away%20semi-final%20match%20against%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20in%20Indore%20and%20Pankaj%20Dharmani%20the%20Ranji%20debut%20in%20the%20final%20against%20Maharashtra%20in%20Ludhiana.%20Sharma%20scored%20a%20fine%20century%20in%20the%20final%20that%20helped%20Punjab%20win%20the%20title.%20%E2%80%9CPaaji%20would%20tell%20us%20that%20%E2%80%98no%20match%20is%20lost%20until%20the%20last%20ball%20is%20bowled%E2%80%99%20and%20that%20%E2%80%98you%20need%2020%20wickets%20to%20win%20a%20match%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20the%2060-year-old%20Gursharan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20best%20memory%20of%20my%20association%20with%20paaji%20is%20that%20when%20I%20scored%20298%20not%20out%20against%20Bengal%20in%20the%201988%2F89%20Ranji%20Trophy%20quarter-final%2C%20paaji%20gave%20me%20shoulder%20and%20leg%20massage%20during%20lunch%20time.%20It%20was%20a%20touching%20gesture.%20He%20would%20treat%20all%20players%20equally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20recalling%20his%20knock%20at%20Eden%20Gardens%2C%20Calcutta.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPunjab%20made%20it%20to%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20finals%20twice%20more%20(1994-95%20and%202004-05)%20but%20lost%20on%20both%20occasions%20%E2%80%93%20to%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%E2%80%99s%20Bombay%20and%20Sanjay%20Bangar%E2%80%99s%20Railways%20respectively.%20In%20the%202004-05%20final%2C%20Dharmani%2C%20given%20the%20break%20by%20Bedi%2C%20was%20captain.%20Later%2C%20Bedi%20also%20took%20up%20roles%20with%20Delhi%20and%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Cricket%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBedi%E2%80%99s%20266%20Test%20wickets%20remained%20an%20Indian%20record%20until%20fast%20bowler%20Kapil%20Dev%20broke%20it%20in%201985-86.%20However%2C%20his%20tally%20still%20remained%20the%20best%20by%20a%20left-arm%20Indian%20spinner%20until%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20surpassed%20it%20in%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20against%20Australia%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fqaiser-mohammad-ali%5C%22%3EQaiser%20Mohammad%20Ali%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20covered%20cricket%20for%20over%20three%20decades%20and%20is%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20He%20tweets%20at%20%40AlwaysCricket.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698156947000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24192911%2F41025108361_0fede34032_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbishan-bedi-world-most-colourful-cricketer-tribute%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20legendary%20spinner%20had%20a%20large%20heart%2C%20was%20compassionate%20and%20went%20out%20of%20his%20way%20to%20help%20other%20cricketers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fbishan-bedi-world-most-colourful-cricketer-tribute%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ancient%20rock%20carvings%20of%20human%20faces%20revealed%20by%20Amazon%20River%20drought%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698156360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-manaus-brazil-carvings_6333323.jpg%3F20231024070231%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fancient-rock-carvings-of-human-faces-revealed-by-amazon-river-drought-12991687%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ancient%20human%20faces%20carved%20into%20stone%20around%202%2C000%20years%20ago%20have%20been%20revealed%20by%20a%20historic%20drought%20along%20the%20Amazon%20River.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fancient-rock-carvings-of-human-faces-revealed-by-amazon-river-drought-12991687%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fancient-rock-carvings-of-human-faces-revealed-by-amazon-river-drought-12991687%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fancient-rock-carvings-of-human-faces-revealed-by-amazon-river-drought-12991687%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%2C%20Bhutan%20Vow%20to%20Conclude%20Border%20Talks%20Soon%3B%20Will%20Have%20Implications%20for%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24173057%2FThe-Wire-53.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EChina%20says%20it%20is%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20Bhutan%20to%20conclude%20the%20ongoing%20boundary%20talks%20%E2%80%9Cas%20soon%20as%20possible%E2%80%9D%20and%20to%20establish%20full%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20the%20Himalayan%20Kingdom.%20The%20development%20also%20has%20implications%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBhutan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%20Tandi%20Dorji%20was%20in%20Beijing%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2023%2C%20to%20hold%20talks%20with%20Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20Wang%20Yi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20conclusion%20of%20boundary%20negotiations%20and%20the%20establishment%20of%20diplomatic%20relations%20between%20China%20and%20Bhutan%20fully%20serve%20the%20long-term%20and%20fundamental%20interests%20of%20the%20country%20and%20nation%20of%20Bhutan.%20China%20is%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20Bhutan%20in%20the%20same%20direction%2C%20seize%20the%20historic%20opportunity%2C%20complete%20this%20important%20process%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%2C%20and%20fix%20and%20develop%20China-Bhutan%20friendly%20relations%20in%20legal%20form%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Feng%2Fzxxx_662805%2F202310%2Ft20231023_11166399.html%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20put%20out%20by%20the%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2014%20nations%20with%20which%20China%20shares%20borders%2C%2012%20countries%20have%20settled%20their%20borders.%20Bhutan%20and%20India%20are%20the%20only%20two%20countries%20with%20which%20border%20disputes%20still%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20statement%2C%20Wang%20Yi%20told%20his%20Bhutanese%20counterpart%2C%20%E2%80%9CChina%20always%20prioritises%20neighbourhood%20diplomacy%20in%20its%20overall%20diplomacy%20and%20adheres%20to%20the%20principle%20that%20all%20countries%2C%20big%20or%20small%2C%20are%20equals.%20China%20respects%20the%20sovereignty%2C%20independence%2C%20and%20territorial%20integrity%20of%20all%20countries%20and%20the%20legitimate%20aspirations%20and%20concerns%20of%20small%20and%20medium-sized%20countries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bhutanese%20foreign%20minister%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Chinese%20statement%2C%20said%20Bhutan%20and%20China%20have%20enjoyed%20a%20traditional%20friendship%2C%20and%20Bhutan%20firmly%20abides%20by%20the%20one-China%20principle%20and%20stands%20ready%20to%20work%20with%20China%20for%20an%20early%20settlement%20of%20the%20boundary%20issue%20and%20advance%20the%20political%20process%20of%20establishing%20diplomatic%20relations.%C2%A0He%20also%20thanked%20China%20for%20%E2%80%9Cits%20strong%20support%20and%20assistance%20to%20Bhutan%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20both%20countries%20set%20up%20a%20%E2%80%98Joint%20Technical%20Group%E2%80%99%20(JTG)%20on%20the%20delimitation%20of%20the%20China-Bhutan%20boundary%20as%20part%20of%20Beijing%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20resolution%20of%20the%20boundary%20issue.%20In%20an%20%E2%80%98Expert%20Group%20Meeting%E2%80%99%20(EGM)%20held%20in%20Beijing%20in%20August%2C%20both%20sides%20had%20agreed%20to%20set%20up%20JTG%2C%20and%20to%20take%20%E2%80%9Csimultaneous%20steps%E2%80%9D%20to%20expedite%20the%20implementation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98three-step%20roadmap%E2%80%99%20that%20will%20lead%20to%20the%20demarcation%20of%20the%20boundary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImplications%20for%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-china-set-up-technical-team-on-delimitation-of-boundary%5C%22%3Easserts%3C%2Fa%3E%20claims%20over%20roughly%20764%20square%20kilometres%20in%20the%20northwestern%20and%20central%20regions%20of%20Bhutan.%20Originally%2C%20the%20dispute%20was%20part%20of%20border%20negotiations%20between%20India%20and%20China.%20However%2C%20direct%20dialogues%20between%20China%20and%20Bhutan%20were%20initiated%20in%201984.%20Since%20then%2C%20over%2024%20rounds%20of%20border%20talks%20and%2012%20rounds%20of%20expert-level%20meetings%20have%20taken%20place%2C%20which%20have%20been%20focusing%20on%20Jakarlung%20and%20Pasamlung%20areas%20in%20north%20Bhutan%2C%20and%20the%20Doklam%20area%20in%20west%20Bhutan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20China%20were%20locked%20in%20an%20intense%20standoff%20over%20Doklam%20in%202017%20for%20about%20two%20months%20after%20China%20began%20laying%20a%20road%20towards%20the%20strategically%20significant%20Jampheri%20ridge%20line.%20While%20India%20considers%20the%20Doklam%20plateau%20as%20Bhutanese%20territory%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20stated%20position%20is%20that%20it%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20its%20Chumbi%20Valley%2C%20located%20between%20Sikkim%20and%20Bhutan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202020%2C%20China%20also%20claimed%20the%20Sakteng%20Wildlife%20Sanctuary%2C%20located%20in%20eastern%20Bhutan%2C%20as%20its%20own.%20The%20region%20also%20shares%20borders%20with%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20in%20India.%20China%20also%20allegedly%20built%20several%20villages%20in%20the%20Bhutanese%20territory%2C%20which%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Lotay%20Tshering%2C%20had%20dismissed%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-india-china-border-lotay-tshering%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Belgian%20newspaper%C2%A0%3Cem%3ELa%20Libre%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETshering%20had%20said%20that%20the%20demarcation%20of%20the%20Bhutan-China%20boundary%20would%20be%20settled%20at%20an%20early%20date%2C%20but%20the%20tri-junction%20point%20with%20India%20would%20be%20dealt%20with%20separately%20with%20the%20inclusion%20of%20India.%20%E2%80%9CDoklam%20is%20a%20junction%20point%20between%20India%2C%20China%20and%20Bhutan.%20It%20is%20not%20up%20to%20Bhutan%20alone%20to%20fix%20the%20problem.%20There%20are%20three%20of%20us.%20There%20is%20no%20big%20or%20small%20country%3B%20all%20are%20three%20equal%20countries%2C%20each%20counting%20for%20one-third%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tshering%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bhutanese%20prime%20minister%20had%20also%20said%20discussions%20on%20the%20tri-junction%20can%20only%20start%20once%20India%20and%20China%20have%20resolved%20their%20differences%20along%20their%20borders.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20ready.%20We%20can%20discuss%20this%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20other%20two%20parties%20are%20ready.%20India%20and%20China%20have%20problems%20all%20along%20their%20border.%20We%20are%20waiting%20to%20see%20how%20they%20will%20settle%20their%20differences%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20India%2C%20Doklam%20holds%20great%20significance%20from%20a%20security%20point%20of%20view.%20China%E2%80%99s%20control%20over%20the%20region%20would%20pose%20a%20threat%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20Siliguri%20Corridor%2C%20a%2022-km%20stretch%20which%20connects%20the%20Indian%20mainland%20to%20the%20Northeast.%20The%20stretch%2C%20commonly%20known%20as%20the%20Chicken%E2%80%99s%20Neck%2C%20links%20India%20with%20Tibet%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698154823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24173057%2FThe-Wire-53.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchina-bhutan-vow-to-conclude-border-talks-soon-will-have-implications-for-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bhutan's%20foreign%20minister%20Tandi%20Dorji%20held%20talks%20with%20Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20Wang%20Yi%20in%20Beijing%20on%20October%2023.%20While%20India%20considers%20the%20strategic%20Doklam%20Plateau%20as%20the%20undisputed%20territory%20of%20Bhutan%2C%20China%20claims%20the%20region%20as%20its%20own.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchina-bhutan-vow-to-conclude-border-talks-soon-will-have-implications-for-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Putin%20'fine'%2C%20Kremlin%20says%20amid%20more%20reports%20of%20illness%20-%20and%20comments%20on%20body%20double%20rumours%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698153780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-vladimir-putin-moscow_6333688.jpg%3F20231024131912%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fvladimir-putin-fine-kremlin-says-amid-more-reports-of-illness-and-comments-on-body-double-rumours-12991661%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Kremlin%20has%20dismissed%20fresh%20speculation%20that%20Russian%20President%20Vladimi