0into%20politics%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20critics%20were%20quick%20to%20point%20out%20that%20he%20is%20assuming%20sweeping%20powers%20with%20almost%20no%20accountability.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20will%20henceforth%20manage%20the%20affairs%20of%20both%20the%20government%20and%20the%20ruling%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD).%20He%20will%20wield%20sweeping%20powers%20and%20be%20answerable%20only%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20who%20has%20always%20given%20him%20a%20free%20hand.%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20position%2C%20thus%2C%20has%20been%20further%20strengthened%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Congress%20veteran%20and%20former%20minister%20Ganeswar%20Behera.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPandian%E2%80%99s%20voluntary%20retirement%20came%20as%20no%20surprise%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20Behera%2C%20who%20have%20been%20watching%20his%20growth%20trajectory%20keenly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20politically%20conscious%20person%20would%20have%20seen%20this%20coming.%20Earlier%2C%20he%20was%20calling%20the%20shots%20from%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20but%20now%20he%20will%20do%20this%20more%20directly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Behera%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fodisha-ias-officer-karthikeyan-pandian-naveen-patnaik-successor%5C%22%3EOdisha%3A%20Is%20IAS%20Officer%20Karthikeyan%20Pandian%20a%20Potential%20Successor%20to%20Naveen%20Patnaik%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20surprising%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20speed%20with%20which%20things%20have%20happened%2C%20taking%20even%20journalists%20by%20surprise.%20The%20letter%20seeking%20VRS%20went%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20October%2020%20and%20he%20was%20relieved%20on%20October%2023%E2%80%9D%2C%20adding%20that%20speculation%20about%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20politics%20was%20natural.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20has%20not%20resigned%20to%20do%20%3Cem%3Etapasya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(penance).%20He%20is%20now%20looking%20to%20legitimise%20his%20authority%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Congress%20veteran%2C%20who%20does%20not%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Sujata%C2%A0also%20putting%20in%20her%20papers%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20into%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFormer%20state%20BJP%20president%20Samir%20Mohanty%20finds%20the%20timing%20of%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20VRS%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20comes%20only%20months%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%20It%20is%20obvious%20that%20he%20will%20be%20managing%20the%20entire%20election%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20BJD.%20He%20did%20this%20earlier%2C%20too%2C%20but%20this%20time%20he%20will%20do%20it%20openly%20and%20directly.%20Henceforth%20he%20will%20be%20running%20both%20the%20government%20and%20the%20BJD%20organisation%20and%20no%20one%20will%20question%20his%20authority%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mohanty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20people%20had%20been%20making%20conjectures%20about%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20resignation%20and%20his%20possible%20entry%20into%20politics%2C%20speculation%20in%20this%20regard%20intensified%20after%20he%20began%20touring%20districts%20using%20a%20state%20helicopter%2C%20which%20drew%20the%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20ire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ace%20bureaucrat%20was%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-soumya-ranjan-patnaik-expelled-media-baron%5C%22%3Etargeted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20BJD%20MLA%20and%20media%20baron%20Soumya%20Ranjan%20Patnaik%2C%20who%20questioned%20his%20visits%20and%20made%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20him%20in%20%3Cem%3ESambad%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Odia%20daily%20founded%20by%20him.%20The%20retaliation%20was%20swift%2C%20with%20Ranjan%20Patnaik%20thrown%20out%20of%20the%20BJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPandian%E2%80%99s%20closeness%20to%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20has%20never%20been%20in%20doubt.%20His%20efficiency%20and%20management%20skills%20were%20the%20talk%20of%20the%20power%20corridors%20in%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20with%20almost%20every%20move%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20bearing%20his%20stamp.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnaveen-odisha-bjd-legacy-biju-patnaik%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Naveen%20Odisha%E2%80%99%3A%20Why%20BJD%20Is%20Moving%20on%20From%20the%20Legacy%20of%20Biju%20Patnaik%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThough%20born%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20he%20has%20an%20Odisha%20connection%3A%20his%20wife%20Sujata%20(nee%20Rout)%20hails%20from%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Kendrapara%20district.%20Her%20father%20Akshay%20Kumar%20Rout%2C%20who%20passed%20away%20in%202020%2C%20was%20an%20eminent%20paediatrician.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPandian%20has%20been%20the%20eyes%20and%20ears%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%20the%20last%2012%20years.%20In%20the%20initial%20years%2C%20he%20took%20utmost%20care%20to%20ensure%20that%20he%20did%20not%20step%20out%20of%20his%20boss%E2%80%99s%20shadow%2C%20but%20slowly%20his%20activities%20earned%20public%20attention%20and%20brought%20him%20into%20focus.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20visits%20to%20different%20districts%20using%20a%20state%20helicopter%20drew%20opposition%20fire%2C%20as%20this%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20a%20bureaucrat%20to%20arrogate%20to%20himself%20the%20powers%20and%20privileges%20of%20a%20public%20representative.%20His%20visits%20drew%20large%20crowds%20and%20ruling%20party%20politicians%20were%20seen%20fawning%20upon%20him%20during%20these%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20though%20the%20chief%20minister%20himself%20clarified%20that%20Pandian%20was%20visiting%20the%20districts%20on%20his%20instructions%2C%20the%20controversy%20refused%20to%20die%20down.%20This%20could%20be%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20he%20took%20VRS%20and%20decided%20to%20assume%20a%20more%20direct%20role%20in%20the%20affairs%20of%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20political%20analyst%20Shashi%20Kant%20Mishra%20who%2C%20however%2C%20dismisses%20the%20speculation%20about%20Pandian%20contesting%20elections%20as%20political%20kite%20flying.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20that%20happening%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20Even%20his%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20Odia%2C%20will%20think%20twice%20before%20taking%20the%20political%20plunge.%20Since%20the%20question%20about%20Naveen%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20successor%20remains%20unanswered%2C%20there%20is%20always%20room%20for%20speculation%2C%E2%80%9D%20added%20Mishra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20261px)%2085vw%2C%20261px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20160942%2FPandian8-237x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22261%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20160942%2FPandian8-237x300.jpg%20237w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F20160942%2FPandian8.jpg%20758w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-659149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22330%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20poster%20on%20Odisha%20government%E2%80%99s%20ambitious%205T%20initiative%20features%20Karthikeyan%20Pandian.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EPandian%E2%80%99s%20efficiency%20as%20a%20bureaucrat%20was%20never%20in%20doubt.%20Apart%20from%20being%20the%20longest-serving%20private%20secretary%20to%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20longest-serving%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20was%20also%20the%205T%20(team%20work%2C%20technology%2C%20transparency%2C%20transformation%20and%20time%20limit)%20secretary%20of%20the%20state%20since%202019%2C%20entrusted%20with%20the%20task%20of%20ensuring%20good%20and%20pro-people%20governance%20with%20complete%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20first%20came%20to%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20notice%20during%20his%20stint%20as%20the%20sub-collector%20of%20Dharamgarh%20in%20Kalahandi%2C%20once%20considered%20the%20proverbial%20backwaters%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20impact%20of%20his%20bold%20administrative%20moves%20was%20felt%20by%20the%20people%20of%20the%20area%2C%20who%20saw%20it%20transform%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPandian%20was%20among%20the%20youngest%20collectors%20in%20the%20country%20when%20he%20took%20charge%20of%20the%20tribal-majority%20Mayurbhanj%20district%2C%20where%20he%20accelerated%20the%20pace%20of%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20his%20most%20satisfying%20and%20fruitful%20tenure%20as%20a%20young%20IAS%20officer%20was%20as%20the%20collector%20of%20Ganjam%2C%20the%20district%20that%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20hails%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20degree%20of%20efficiency%20and%20transparency%20with%20which%20he%20implemented%20the%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme%20(NREGS)%20in%20the%20district%20helped%20reduce%20the%20scale%20of%20labour%20migration%20from%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20came%20up%20with%20innovative%20ideas%20like%20the%20transfer%20of%20wages%20to%20bank%20accounts%2C%20thus%20ruling%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20Pandian%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Sujata%20heads%20the%20newly%20created%20department%20of%20Mission%20Shakti%2C%20which%20aims%20at%20making%20women%20self-reliant%2C%20the%20couple%20is%20crucial%20to%20the%20political%20fortunes%20of%20Patnaik%E2%80%99s%20BJD.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMission%20Shakti%20supports%20more%20than%2070%20lakh%20women%20organised%20under%20six%20lakh%20women%E2%80%99s%20self-help%20groups%2C%20which%20constitute%20a%20key%20vote-bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fashutoshmishra%5C%22%3EAshutosh%20Mishra%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20an%20Odisha-based%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698151241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F24161711%2FV.-K.-Pandian.jpeg%22%2C%22