%20department%20and%20the%20HIV%20patients%20to%20the%20referral%20centre%20in%20Kanpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20for%20a%20period%20of%20time%20after%20someone%20was%20infected%2C%20the%20virus%20cannot%20be%20detected%20by%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%20of%20transfusion%2C%20the%20doctors%20should%20have%20%5Balso%5D%20vaccinated%20the%20children%20against%20Hepatitis%20B%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20%3Cem%3EHT%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDistrict-level%20officials%20will%20trace%20the%20root%20of%20infection%20under%20the%20Viral%20Hepatitis%20Control%20Programme.%20The%20team%20will%20look%20for%20the%20place%20of%20infection%2C%20both%20for%20hepatitis%20and%20HIV%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20senior%20official%20of%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20National%20Health%20Mission%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698149337000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F05%2F23155100%2F6967743623_3d16ff7619_z.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Futtar-pradesh-14-children-infected-with-hiv-and-hepatitis-after-blood-transfusion%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20children%20received%20transfusions%20at%20various%20private%20and%20district%20hospitals%20for%20thalassemia%2C%20a%20blood%20disorder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Futtar-pradesh-14-children-infected-with-hiv-and-hepatitis-after-blood-transfusion%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RSS%20Chief%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%3A%20How%20Did%20Manipur%20Violence%20Continue%20Unabated%20Despite%20a%20Strong%20Government%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F08234700%2FIMG_1535.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20