%3Fp%3D332837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20brainchild%20of%20Sudha%20Iyengar%2C%20Siddhi%20Creations%20was%20a%20venture%20to%20keep%20young%20children%20engaged%20fruitfully%20and%20joyfully%20during%20summer%20vacations%20while%20also%20picking%20up%20on%20essential%20life%20skills.%20With%20managing%20her%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%20condition%2C%20Sudha's%20smile%20for%20everyone%20who%20enters%20her%20home%20has%20been%20winning%20hearts%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20decades.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332837%2Fbengaluru-multiple-sclerosis-summer-camps-hobby-classes-sudha-iyengar-senior-citizen%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Doctor%20or%20a%20Standup%20Comedian%3F%20Dr%20Pal%20Manickam%20On%20Using%20Laughter%20As%20Medicine%20For%20Millions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHey%2C%20after%20this%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20going%20to%20know%20you%20inside%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Palaniappan%20Manickam%20tells%20his%20patient%20before%20doing%20an%20endoscopy%2C%20making%20the%20patient%20laugh.%20The%20gastroenterologist%2C%20based%20out%20of%20Sacramento%20in%20California%2C%20USA%2C%20uses%20humour%20to%20make%20patients%20feel%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUntil%202020%2C%20only%20his%20patients%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327134%2Fqueer-comedian-navin-noronha-on-navigating-comedy-circuit-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappreciated%20his%20humour%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20thanks%20to%20social%20media%2C%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20laughing%20with%20him.%20In%20March%202020%2C%20his%20video%20on%20COVID-19%20went%20viral%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20a%20genre%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%98Medcom%E2%80%99%20(medical%20comedy).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20positive%20response%20to%20his%20initial%20video%20led%20the%20doctor%20to%20create%20many%20videos%2C%20which%20focus%20on%20important%20medical%20topics%2C%20infused%20with%20humour%20to%20make%20them%20more%20palatable.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20around%20two%20million%20subscribers%20across%20YouTube%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20come%20to%20a%20gastroenterologist%20with%20diseases%20like%20haemorrhoids%20and%20piles%2C%20which%20they%20find%20embarrassing%20to%20describe.%20When%20patients%20have%20to%20discuss%20stool%20habits%2C%20related%20changes%2C%20acidity%20etc%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20open%20up%20right%20away.%20So%20I%20started%20breaking%20the%20ice%20using%20a%20joke.%20They%20loved%20it%2C%20so%20I%20stuck%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Pal%2C%20as%20he%20is%20fondly%20called%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20appreciation%20for%20the%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20humour%20boosted%20his%20morale%20and%20opened%20up%20doors%20for%20him%20at%20a%20standup%20comedy%20club%20in%20Bay%20Area%2C%20California%2C%20called%20%E2%80%98Building%2018%E2%80%99.%20This%20kicked%20off%20the%2039-year-old%E2%80%99s%20stint%20as%20a%20comedian.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20joined%20Building%2018%20in%20May%202020%20and%20learnt%20tips%20and%20tricks%20on%20how%20to%20write%20a%20script%2C%20how%20to%20deliver%20a%20punch%2C%20what%20is%20stand-up%20comedy%20and%20much%20more.%20I%20found%20this%20to%20be%20much%20more%20difficult%20than%20medicine%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20first%20standup%20show%20at%20the%20club%2C%20Dr%20Pal%20describes%20the%20experience%20as%20%E2%80%9Cincomparable%E2%80%9D.%20He%20says%20he%20spent%20hours%20preparing%20for%20his%2010-minute%20set%2C%20where%20he%20spoke%20about%20many%20serious%20medical%20issues%20in%20a%20comical%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20grab%20this%20chance%20that%20life%20had%20given%20him%2C%20the%20doctor%20dove%20head%20first%20into%20comedy%2C%20creating%20reels%20and%20videos%2C%20and%20doing%20shows.%20Today%2C%20he%20does%20his%20%E2%80%98medcom%E2%80%99%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20in%20the%20US%2C%20India%2C%20Malaysia%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20punchline%20for%20a%20health%20tip%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5_1yhDaDZfA%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F5_1yhDaDZfA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Dr%20Pal%20started%20his%20YouTube%20journey%20with%20a%20video%20about%20COVID%2C%20what%20really%20catapulted%20him%20to%20fame%20was%20his%20video%20on%20intermittent%20fasting%2C%20where%20he%20shared%20his%20own%20weight%20loss%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20started%20when%20the%20doctor%20had%20a%20health%20scare%20which%20made%20him%20sit%20up%20and%20take%20notice.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20100%20kg%20then%20and%20had%20palpitations%20while%20working.%20I%20realised%20how%20hypocritical%20I%20was%3B%20not%20practising%20what%20I%20was%20preaching.%20I%20had%20been%20studying%20medicine%20for%20almost%2015%20years%20but%20had%20forgotten%20to%20take%20care%20of%20my%20health%20in%20the%20process.%20I%20tried%20every%20diet%20but%20nothing%20worked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20started%20a%20research%20programme%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327558%2Frevant-himatsingka-foodpharmer-shares-how-to-read-food-labels-for-health-risks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintermittent%20fasting%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20few%20of%20his%20patients%20who%20had%20fatty%20liver.%20As%20the%20programme%20progressed%2C%20the%20doctor%20also%20started%20practising%20the%20same%20in%20his%20personal%20life.%20After%20losing%20almost%2025%20kg%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20share%20the%20lessons%20he%20learned%20with%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20had%20such%20a%20tough%20time%20losing%20weight.%20I%20wondered%20how%20tough%20it%20is%20for%20non-medical%20people.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20started%20making%20reels%20on%20Instagram%20to%20help%20people%20learn%20healthy%20habits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20delivers%20these%20important%20messages%20%E2%80%94%20about%20gut%20health%2C%20fatty%20liver%2C%20heart%20health%2C%20foods%20to%20consume%2C%20and%20tips%20for%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20comic%20element.%20To%20help%20deliver%20the%20message%20better%2C%20he%20created%20some%20imaginary%20characters%20like%20%E2%80%98Saravana%20Kumar%E2%80%99%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20like%20following%20a%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Eat%20between%20sunrise%20and%20sunset%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCt1TuJ3LM_r%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCt1TuJ3LM_r%2F%3Fu