0the%20place.%20From%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20was%20not%20going%20to%20add%20to%20the%20carbon%20footprint.%20Instead%2C%20I%20would%20try%20to%20minimise%20it%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPromoting%20slow%20and%20sustainable%20tourism%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunando%20wakes%20up%20with%20the%20sun%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331901%2Fcouple-quit-job-to-build-eco-friendly-carbon-negative-home-homestay-in-himachal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreathtaking%20view%20of%20the%20Himalayas.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Once%20he%20is%20up%2C%20he%20takes%20his%20five%20dogs%20on%20a%20stroll%20to%20enjoy%20nature%20and%20hopefully%20spot%20some%20animals.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20Corbett%20is%20a%20valley%2C%20we%20are%20on%20top%20of%20a%20hill.%20So%20we%20get%20a%20striking%20view%20of%20the%20mountains%2C%20and%20we%20also%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20animal%20spottings.%20Walking%20with%20my%20dogs%20and%20enjoying%20the%20silence%20of%20the%20woods%20is%20my%20favourite%20part%20of%20the%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1697812224.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20has%20a%20stunning%20view%20of%20the%20Himalayas.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1697812224.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1697812224-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1697812224-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1697812224-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Ftanhau-1697812224-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332762%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%20has%20a%20stunning%20view%20of%20the%20Himalayas.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Tanhau%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20his%20life%20was%20the%20opposite%20of%20this.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20stuck%20in%20the%20corporate%20cycle%20in%20an%20office%20that%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20in.%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%20the%20wild%20and%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20Sunando%20completed%20his%20education%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Kolkata%20before%20working%20as%20a%20banker.%20%E2%80%9CI%20worked%20for%20over%20two%20decades%20as%20a%20banker%20and%20also%20had%20a%20successful%20startup.%20I%20worked%20hard%20for%20so%20many%20years%2C%20so%20I%20can%20afford%20to%20live%20the%20life%20I%20want%20now.%20In%202011%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20sell%20my%20startup%20and%20purchase%20land%20in%20Corbett%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPacking%20his%20life%20and%20moving%20to%20the%20mountains%2C%20which%20is%20every%20other%20city%20dweller%E2%80%99s%20dream%20became%20Sunando%E2%80%99s%20reality.%20All%20he%20needed%20to%20do%20was%20find%20the%20perfect%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20an%20inclination%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F234711%2Fhow-does-india-protect-tigers-fateh-singh-rathore-ranthambhore-national-park-rajasthan-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etowards%20Corbett%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20the%20start%20because%20it%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20places%20I%20ever%20saw%20the%20big%20cat.%20Additionally%2C%20Corbett%20is%20the%20best%20example%20of%20nature%20at%20its%20best.%20I%20have%20been%20to%20many%20other%20national%20parks%20too%2C%20but%20I%20always%20found%20Corbett%20more%20beautiful%20than%20any%20place%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20few%20visits%2C%20he%20found%20a%20five-acre%20land%20in%20a%20small%20village%20called%20Bhatoli%20in%20the%20Corbett%20area.%20Sunando%20decided%20to%20build%20an%20eco-friendly%20home.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20was%20in%20bad%20shape%20when%20we%20bought%20it.%20The%20trees%20and%20wildlife%20near%20it%20were%20mostly%20destroyed.%20So%20we%20started%20with%20planting%20500%20trees%20and%20making%20the%20place%20green%20again%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20over%20the%20years%2C%20he%20has%20planted%20more%20than%205%2C000%20trees%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20house%20is%20done%20using%20locally%20sourced%20stones%20and%20%3Cem%3Emitti%20%3C%2Fem%3E(mud)%20from%20the%20area.%20We%20wanted%20to%20support%20the%20local%20communities%20around%20the%20area%3B%20hence%2C%20we%20only%20employed%20people%20from%20the%20villages%20to%20help%20us%20construct%20the%20homestay%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20all%20materials%20were%20locally%20sourced%2C%20and%20the%20homestay%20solely%20hires%20local%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAdditionally%2C%2095%20percent%20of%20the%20homestay%20is%20running%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F173892%2Fbengaluru-sustainable-home-solar-power-rainwater-harvesting-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20solar%20energy.%3C%2Fa%3E%20There%20are%20only%20a%20few%20things%20that%20require%20electricity.%20We%20also%20do%20rainwater%20harvesting%20and%20have%20a%20storage%20capacity%20of%201%2C00%2C000%20litres%20of%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22