erson%20from%20Karnataka%20wants%20to%20buy%20%3Cem%3Ekulhads%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20will%20locate%20the%20plant%20set%20up%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20connect%20the%20two.%20This%20way%20the%20customer%20gets%20the%20product%20faster%20and%20without%20any%20damages%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShobhit%20has%20set%20up%20over%2045%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplants%20across%20India%20in%20states%20including%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%20etc.%20He%20is%20also%20setting%20up%20one%20plant%20in%20Canada%20which%20will%20be%20launched%20in%20January%20next%20year.%20By%20setting%20up%20plants%20in%20different%20states%2C%20he%20has%20formed%20a%20network%20of%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad-%3C%2Fem%3Emakers%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENot%20his%20first%20attempt%20at%20business%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20Shobhit%20informs%20that%20he%20has%20tried%20his%20hand%20at%20various%20types%20of%20businesses%20before%20finding%20success%20with%20Mittisa.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20was%20in%20college%2C%20I%20started%20a%20course%20where%20I%20taught%20students%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F85389%2Fwhy-effective-communication-can-make-big-difference%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20communication%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20earned%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2022%20lakhs%20in%20a%20year.%20Then%2C%20I%20started%20an%20AI%20company%20but%20it%20had%20to%20be%20shut%20down%20due%20to%20a%20dispute%20among%20the%20co-founders%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%20there%20was%20the%20%3Cem%3Echai%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebusiness%20before%20I%20started%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebusiness.%20You%20never%20know%20what%20would%20hit%20the%20right%20nerve%20in%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESomething%20as%20simple%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekulhad%20%3C